        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post 3 Bedroom / 2 Bathroom Home for Rent – Glendale, AZ Rent: $1,050/month Security Deposit: $1,050 Size: 1,302 sq. ft. Now available! This well-maintained 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home offers 1,302 square feet of comfortable living space in a convenient Glendale location. The home features a spacious living area, a functional kitchen with plenty of cabinet space, and a private primary bedroom with an en-suite bathroom. The additional bedrooms are generously sized and perfect for family, guests, or a home office. Features: 3 Bedrooms 2 Full Bathrooms 1,302 Sq. Ft. Open living and dining area Spacious kitchen with ample storage Central heating and air conditioning Washer/Dryer hookups Private backyard Off-street parking Conveniently located near schools, shopping, dining, and major freeways Monthly Rent: $1,050 Security Deposit: $1,050 No smoking. Pets may be considered with approval. Call or message today to schedule a showing or for more information. This home won't last long!",
