        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Move-in Specials at Obsidian on Glendale 1 and 2 bedroom floor plan - 8 weeks concession. 3 bedroom floor plan receives a $2,000.00 concession.Call us for Details! **Restrictions apply. Please contact leasing for more details. 7601 W Glendale Ave, Glendale, AZ 85303 Explore a lavish apartment community at Obsidian on Glendale. Offering a masterfully tailored range of one, two and three-bedroom floor plans— Obsidian on Glendale and our apartments in Glendale, AZ for rent are the complete package for your luxury lifestyle. When you enter your apartment’s interiors you’ll be greeted with spacious floor plans, open lighting and state-of-the-art appliances. Enjoy a daily routine of yoga in the fitness center, an afternoon relaxing by the pool and a delectable dinner in your Gourmet Chef Kitchen. Conveniently located in Glendale, the sunset views are hard to escape and the metro access is a short distance from the community. Obsidian on Glendale has it all, crafted just for you. Unit Amenities: Gourmet Chef Kitchen Private Patio or Balcony for Every Apartment Large Walk-In Closets with Built-in Shelving Dual Vanities Full-Sized In-Home Washer & Dryer Stainless Steel Kitchen Appliances Modern 2” Wood-Style Blinds Eco-Friendly Dual Paned Windows *In Select Homes Community Amenities: Self-Service Package Lockers Pet Friendly with Bark Park and Pet Wash Clubhouse Poolside Pavilion with BBQ Grills Valet Trash and Recycling Service Expansive Fitness Center with Yoga Studio Outdoor Game Lounge with Corn Hole Gated and Smoke-Free Community Call: show contact info Website: https://livecushwake.com/m5pd6h2h/obsidian-on-glendale *Equal housing opportunity*",
