        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Garden Terrace offers a secure living environment with gated access and controlled entry for added peace of mind. Residents can enjoy a variety of amenities, including a spacious pool and outdoor courtyard with BBQ pits, perfect for relaxing or entertaining. The community features updated interiors with tile flooring, ceiling fans, and full kitchens equipped with dishwashers, all designed for comfort and convenience. Walk-in closets and balconies or yards provide additional space, while laundry facilities offer practicality for daily living. Located near the ASU Main Campus, the community provides easy access to downtown cultural venues, galleries, museums, and live theatre performances. - Laundry Facilities - LOW Pet Rent - Included Water, Sewer and Trash - Covered, Assigned Parking - Large, Comfortable Pool - Controlled Access - Tile Flooring Residents can take advantage of covered, assigned parking and gated outdoor areas with grills for outdoor gatherings. The professional management team ensures a well-maintained and clean environment, and residents benefit from included water, sewer, and trash services. With numerous local franchises supporting NFL, MLB, NBA, and NHL games, there's plenty of entertainment nearby. Garden Terrace truly combines comfort, convenience, and a vibrant community atmosphere. Ask about our Availability Today Reach Out Today Garden Terrace 4848 E Holly Street Phone: show contact info",
