        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Move-in Specials at Obsidian on Glendale 1 bedroom floor plan - 8 weeks concession.2 bedroom floor plan - 4 weeks concession. 3 bedroom floor plan receives a $2,000.00 concession.Call us for Details! **Restrictions apply. Please contact leasing for more details. 7601 W Glendale Ave, Glendale, AZ 85303 Explore a lavish apartment community at Obsidian on Glendale. Offering a masterfully tailored range of one, two and three-bedroom floor plans— Obsidian on Glendale and our apartments in Glendale, AZ for rent are the complete package for your luxury lifestyle. When you enter your apartment’s interiors you’ll be greeted with spacious floor plans, open lighting and state-of-the-art appliances. Enjoy a daily routine of yoga in the fitness center, an afternoon relaxing by the pool and a delectable dinner in your Gourmet Chef Kitchen. Conveniently located in Glendale, the sunset views are hard to escape and the metro access is a short distance from the community. Obsidian on Glendale has it all, crafted just for you. Unit Amenities: Full-Sized In-Home Washer & Dryer Eco-Friendly Dual Paned Windows Prep Islands & Pendant Lighting Granite Countertops Elegant Hardwood-Style Flooring Gourmet Chef Kitchen Modern 2” Wood-Style Blinds Large Walk-In Closets with Built-in Shelving *In Select Homes Community Amenities: Heated Pool with Private Cabanas Poolside Pavilion with BBQ Grills Pet Friendly with Bark Park and Pet Wash Outdoor Game Lounge with Corn Hole Fire Pit with Seating Area Kids Play Zone with Playground Self-Service Package Lockers Expansive Fitness Center with Yoga Studio Call: show contact info Website: https://livecushwake.com/r3my64zj/obsidian-on-glendale *Equal housing opportunity*",
