        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post 2102 W Dunlap Ave, Phoenix, AZ 85021 Stay at Emerald Suites Dunlap in Phoenix, Arizona, with all of the comforts of home, at an affordable price, and all utilities included. Our living spaces offer the comfort and essentials you need, perfect for a few weeks or an extended stay. Each room features a handy kitchenette equipped with a full-sized fridge, microwave, stove top, and dining area. Nestled in a prime location, our extended stay apartment community provides easy access to a myriad of exciting attractions. Immerse yourself in the rich cultural experiences at the Phoenix Art Museum or catch a thrilling game at the nearby State Farm Stadium. Indulge in retail therapy at the bustling Biltmore Fashion Park or explore the stunning landscapes of the Desert Botanical Garden. For family fun, visit the Phoenix Zoo or embark on a scenic hike at Camelback Mountain. !$399 MOVE IN SPECIAL! Features Include: On Call Maintenance for Emergencies Onsite Laundry Facilities Easy Access to I-10, I-17, 51, and 101 Freeways Parking Included Complimentary Coffee Daily Utilities Included Stove Top Modern Paint Scheme Furnished Suites Dishwasher Microwave Flat Screen TVs with Cable Channels Call: show contact info For more information, visit us at: https://liveamgnevada.com/f2j3yrze/emerald-suites-dunlap-ave Pricing and availability are subject to change daily. Photos may not be of the exact advertised unit. Contact us today for the most up to date information.",
