        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post Pricing: 1095 Bed: 1 Bath: 1 Papago Fairways offers a comfortable and secure living environment with numerous amenities designed for convenience and relaxation. Residents can enjoy a large, inviting swimming pool and lush putting greens, perfect for leisure and outdoor activities. The community features spacious apartments with vaulted ceilings, walk-in closets, and an eat-in kitchen with modern appliances such as a dishwasher. For added convenience, there is an onsite laundry center, extra storage options, and covered, assigned parking spaces. Papago Fairways show contact info 5343 E Taylor St Putting Greens Laundry Facilities Pets Always Welcome! Vaulted Ceilings Elevator for Upper Level Apartments Fireplace Eat-in Kitchen Gated Included Water, Sewer and Trash Elevator access makes upper-level units easily accessible, while the gated community ensures safety and peace of mind. Utilities including water, sewer, and trash are included in the rent, simplifying monthly bills. A professional management team is available onsite to assist residents, and pets are welcome with low monthly rent. With its quiet atmosphere and numerous amenities, Papago Fairways provides a quality living experience in the vibrant Phoenix area.",
