        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Bedrooms:  2 Bathrooms:  2.5 Square Feet:  1193 Address:  202 S Hardy Dr The search for your perfect home ends at the newly renovated Dolce Villagio Townhomes. With thoughtfully designed interiors, inviting amenities, and a prime location, our newly renovated townhomes in Tempe, AZ offer a lifestyle that feels effortlessly comfortable. Whether you're unwinding in a beautifully renovated space, taking advantage of modern conveniences, or exploring the vibrant surroundings, you'll find that everything here is newly designed with your needs in mind. Dolce Villagio Townhomes is at the epicenter of all things Tempe, come experience small community living with very large comforts. The small-town feel and hip vibe of Tempe make your new place at Dolce a great place to live. Enjoy the array of activities at Tempe Town Lake hiking, biking, paddle boarding and year-round festivals at the nearby Riverwalk, Tempe's Mill Avenue District and Arizona State University. Don't miss any of the Sun Devil home games, the stadium is just a short distance away. We are close to the light rail so you can easily get to downtown Phoenix, midtown and uptown for work or entertainment. Come see Dolce Villagio Townhomes, it's all here! Amenities Include: New Stainless Steel Appliances Newly Renovated Apartments Updated Island Kitchen with Quartz Countertops (In Select Apartments) Loft-Style Townhomes Air Conditioning Ceiling Fan Minutes From Tempe Marketplace White Cabinetry Throughout The Kitchen Carpet Flooring Close to Tempe Town Lake & Tempe Center for the Arts Plank Flooring Throughout Two-Tone Interior Paint Call: show contact info For more information, visit us at: https://cal-amliving.com/vg6zpvoh/dolce-villagio",
