        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Fabulous 5bed/3bath Home in the sought after Estates at Spectrum community. This Smart Floor-Plan includes Generous master suite w/double Door Entry, Separate Tub & Shower, Dual Sinks & Walk-in Closet. Home features Bedroom and Full Bath downstairs, Upstairs Laundry and Large Loft! Open Kitchen with Newly Installed Granite Countertop, extended cabinetry with detailed crown molding, stainless steel appliances, breakfast bar/island and dual pantries. Backyard with Extended Covered Patio, with Automatic Sun-Screens, Pavers, Fire-Pit, and Garden Boxes. Brand New Exterior/interior Paint, RV gate and nice Landscaping in Front and Backyard. Private lot with only one neighbor and huge park beside and behind home. Excellent neighborhood with playgrounds & neighborhood parks! Home is in the #1 school district in AZ Moments from the 202 freeway, San Tan Village - New carpets - Thriving well maintained community in Gilbert located at SW side of Val Vista and Germann Rd. - Amazing location! - Only 1-2 minutes from SanTan 202 freeway. - Less than 5 minutes from Mercy Gilbert Hospital, Santan Shopping Mall, Costco, Lowes, Home Depot, Trader Joes, Sprouts, Public Library, Movie theatres, Target, Restaurants, all major banks and so much more. Walking distance to Church. Kumon is right in this intersection. - Nearest schools: Weinberg (walking distance) and Haley elementary, Campo Verde Junior High, Perry high school (walking distance). Chandler Unified School District. - Nice walking paths throughout community, playground, tot-lot within walking distance. Basketball court just behind the home. - If you are thinking of luxury and convenience, this house has everything you need. Home Features: - 5br/3ba, Living, Family, Kitchen and Breakfast Nook. Two story. 2,732 sqft. Built 2005. - Gourmet kitchen with upgraded cabinet, stainless steel appliances and Newly Installed Granite Countertop. - Master bathroom w/ garden tub, double sink, and a separate walk-in shower. - Large family room with lots of windows and a sliding door for light and back yard view. - Refrigerator is included. - Washer & Dryer will be provided if needed. - Wooden blinds installed throughout the house. - Upgraded insulation and Low-Energy windows save on your energy bill. - Automatic sun shade screens installed to save on energy bill. - Ceiling fans installed in all bedrooms, family room and loft to save on energy bill. Four ceiling fans installed in the extended patio for comfort. - Lush and low maintenance front and back yard. Green areas and colorful flowers. - Big backyard and side-yards in the large lot size of 7285 sq ft . - 2-car garage with built in shelves for storage. - Shelves in laundry room gives added storage space. - 10 feet exterior gate. - All appliances come with full warranty - Utilities: Tenant pays for electricity, gas (water heating), Gilbert utility (water, sewer, recycle, trash) - Smoking: This is a non-smoking house. - Pets: Only well trained dogs and cats (no wild animals!), renter is responsible for damage done by pets. - Security deposit: Equal to one month's rent, fully refundable. - Pet fee: $150/cat and $250/dog. - Credit check fees: $35/per adult. - Landscaping: Tenant maintains it. - Owner pays monthly HOA fees - 0.0% Gilbert city residential rental tax until or unless tax law changes.",
