        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Welcome to this charming 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home. This house features a variety of amenities including a dishwasher, washer/dryer hookups, 2 car garage, gas wall heater, swamp cooler, refrigerator, fireplace, and a built-in microwave. The property boasts tile floors in both bathrooms and kitchen and Luxury Vinyl Plank flooring throughout, as well as lots of cabinet space for storage. Enjoy the convenience of a gas range and ceiling fans in each room. The fenced back yard provides privacy and space for outdoor activities. Located near shopping centers and restaurants, this home is situated in the desirable Enterprise School District. Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity to make this house your new home! Interested renters can message their phone number anytime.",
