        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post This modern home features 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, perfect for those seeking a comfortable and stylish living space. With a spacious office, central HVAC, and a fenced back yard, this home offers both functionality and charm. The kitchen is equipped with top-of-the-line appliances including a refrigerator, microwave, dishwasher, and gas stove top. Enjoy the benefits of solar energy, a 3 car garage, ceiling fans, and luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout. The split floor plan and open concept layout create a seamless flow from room to room. With walk-in closets and modern fixtures, this home is the epitome of contemporary living. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this house your home! Interested renters can message their phone number anytime.",
