        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Gated 2-Bed, 2-Bath condominium 461 W Holmes Ave, 347, Mesa, AZ 85210 1600.00 / Month 2 BEDROOMS | 2 BATHROOMS Interested? Fill out this form : https://renter.turbotenant.com/general-prescreener/T3duZXI6NDAzNDA0?property=1817506&source=cl Have questions? Contact the Landlord : https://rental.turbotenant.com/p/461-w-holmes-ave-mesa-az-unit-347/b7b83ee8-2844-406d-947c-f54c250f6532?source=craigslist Property Description: Enjoy comfort and convenience in this gated, beautifully updated CONDO with vaulted ceilings. Featuring new appliances, in-unit washer & dryer, and a private outdoor patio. Community Perks: * No extra fees—water, parking, garbage, & sewage included! * 4 Pools,Hot Tubs, and Outdoor Grills * Clubhouse * Covered Parking Spot * Fiber optic internet for fast, reliable connection! * Located just 1 minute from US60, with easy access to shopping plazas, Mesa Comm College, hospitals, and more. Crime-free community. Property Type : Condo Pets : Small Dogs, Cats Allowed Smoking : NO Lease Term : 1600.00 / Month 2100.00 Deposit Lease Length: One Year Available: 08/01/2026 Occupancy Limit: 3 People Utilities Included : Sewage Water Garbage Appliances : Dishwasher Garbage Disposal Refrigerator Dryer Microwave Washer Freezer Range Oven Amenities : Swimming Pool Vaulted Ceiling Hottub Spa Security Cameras Heating & Cooling : Other Heatpump Central Interested? Fill out this form : https://renter.turbotenant.com/general-prescreener/T3duZXI6NDAzNDA0?property=1817506&source=cl Have questions? Contact the Landlord : https://rental.turbotenant.com/p/461-w-holmes-ave-mesa-az-unit-347/b7b83ee8-2844-406d-947c-f54c250f6532?source=craigslist",
