        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post 4910 W Glenn Dr, Glendale, AZ 85301 If you’re looking for maintenance-free living in Glendale, Arizona, take a look at our comfortable studio, one, and two bedroom homes. Located in a highly sought-after neighborhood in Maricopa County, you’ll be surrounded by ample shopping, dining, and recreation. The best part of joining an affordable 62+ community is that you can relish the day alongside a group of neighbors all celebrating their golden years together. Take advantage of travel, leisure, hobbies, and forging new connections without the hassle of landscaping and house upkeep with an apartment at The Cascalote. Glendale is your home, and it’s time to make the most of the city you love. The Cascalote affords more time to do it all, with a convenient location that keeps you close to everything. Stay close to your connections in town, and enjoy easy access to your favorite grocery store, shops, and local fare. Learn more about our great location on our Neighborhood page, or call now to schedule an in-person tour of our affordable 62+ community in Maricopa County. Apartment Features: ADA Accessible Apartments Available Ceiling Fans Spacious Private Balconies for Indoor/Outdoor Living Air Conditioning High-Speed Internet Available Energy-Efficient Appliances Expansive Kitchen Prep Space Including Quartz Counter Tops Luxury Vinyl Plank, Low Pile Carpet in Bedrooms Elevators Community Features: Free Covered Parking Controlled Access Community Dog Park Covered Patio Overlooking Community Courtyard Community Garden Community Room with Kitchen Resident Services Lighted Walking Path Through Community Picnic Areas with Community Grills Non-Smoking Community Call: show contact info For more information, visit us at: https://livewithmercyhousing.com/blle7reb/cascalote Pricing and availability are subject to change daily. Photos may not be of the exact advertised unit. Contact us today for the most up to date information.",
