        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post 1530 1/2 Diamond St 4 1530 E Diamond St , 4, Phoenix, AZ 85006 1300.00 / Month 1 BEDROOMS | 1 BATHROOMS Interested? Fill out this form : https://renter.turbotenant.com/general-prescreener/T3duZXI6MTAyOTAzMg==?property=2724276&source=cl Have questions? Contact the Landlord : https://rental.turbotenant.com/p/1530-e-diamond-st-phoenix-az-unit-4/00463cf5-204c-4616-959a-3c887841ddb6?source=craigslist Property Description: PLEASE READ ENTIRE DESCRIPTION BEFORE APPLYING. PLEASE ANSWER QUESTIONS BELOW WHEN CONTACTING. Newly remodeled, modern, all-inclusive apartment, with a beautiful view of downtown Phoenix, perfect for one individual. Private gated yard, private balcony, remote-controlled entrance and off street private parking. Enjoy the privacy and security of a gated property with coded access, offering peace of mind while still being part of a quiet, friendly small-community atmosphere. Private and quiet upstairs unit with respectful, easygoing neighbors and a comfortable sense of community without sacrificing personal space. Available Aug 10th. BASE UTILITIES AND INTERNET COVERED BY LANDLORD (Gas, trash, base electric, water, landscaping PLUS Cox internet!) Base electric included in rent - $1400/mo. Tenant responsible for separately metered AC electricity usage- new efficient minisplit units. Unfurnished. Lots of built in storage. Washer and dryer on site. IF INTERESTED: Message with the following info to be invited for tour: - Tell us a little about yourself - When are you looking to move? - Income and employment length? - Animals? - When are you available to tour? - Anything on your credit/background/prior evictions? - Anything else you would like to share? Quaint historic apartment, studio, 1 bathroom, single person guesthouse unit in the heart of Downtown Phoenix. Located just east of Banner Good Samaritan Hospital. Walking/biking distance to all downtown amenities and locally owned restaurants. Next to Ranch Market Grocery store. Close to 51, I10 and 202 Highways. 1 off-street parking space behind automated gate. Not furnished. New electric, plumbing, new Mini-split AC/Heating, new paint and tile, new kitchen and appliances, built-in storage with flat-screen swivel TV, private porch and private fenced in garden. On-site, washer and dryer. Citrus trees. Large communal back yard, complete with picnic table and owner maintained landscaping in both front and back. Property Type : Townhouse Pets : Small Dogs, Cats Allowed Smoking : OUTSIDE_ONLY Lease Term : 1300.00 / Month 1400.00 Deposit Lease Length: One Year Available: 08/12/2026 Occupancy Limit: 1 People Utilities Included : Gas Sewage Water Internet Recycling Garbage Electricity Appliances : Freezer Refrigerator Washer Garbage Disposal Microwave Range Oven Amenities : Balcony Or Deck Fenced Yard Secure Building Heating & Cooling : Other Other Interested? Fill out this form : https://renter.turbotenant.com/general-prescreener/T3duZXI6MTAyOTAzMg==?property=2724276&source=cl Have questions? Contact the Landlord : https://rental.turbotenant.com/p/1530-e-diamond-st-phoenix-az-unit-4/00463cf5-204c-4616-959a-3c887841ddb6?source=craigslist",
