        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Bedrooms:  0 Bathrooms:  1 Square Feet:  638 Address:  1935 S Santan Village Pkwy Find your balance at Elevation at the Village—where luxury living meets laid-back Arizona charm. Nestled in the center of Gilbert, our studio, one-, and two-bedroom apartments are designed for comfort, connection, and everyday ease. With thoughtful features, resort-inspired amenities, and easy access to local shopping, dining, and the 202, this is the lifestyle you’ve been looking for. Offering a selection of studio, one-, and two-bedroom luxury apartments for rent, Elevation at the Village gives residents a prime experience in the best community in the area. Relaxation and recreation are at the forefront with a resort-style pool with a spa and cabanas, an on-site dog park with a pet spa, and a two-level fitness center with state-of-the-art equipment. Inside your spacious home, easily unwind with the latest features: modern kitchens with quartz countertops and tile backsplashes, an in-unit washer/dryer, and private garages are all a given. We are pet-friendly, so your four-legged friends can roam around the neighborhood. Elevation at the Village is ideally located near South Santan Village Parkway and East Williams Field Road, allowing you to reach some of the area’s best destinations within minutes. We’re set right next to popular shopping and entertainment destinations, including SanTan Village Marketplace, Hale Centre Theatre, and Topgolf, while the city’s thriving downtown is within a comfortable ride. Amenities Include: Social Lounge with Arcade Games Vinyl Plank Flooring Bike Storage Amazon Package Lockers Side-by-Side Refrigerators Backlit LED Mirrors Private Garages Available Onsite Storage Units (unclutter your home with convenient storage solutions) Washer/Dryer Elevators Outdoor Seating Areas with Gas Grills Quartz Countertops with Tile Backsplashes Call: show contact info For more information, visit us at: https://cal-amliving.com/hmviu3cg/elevation-at-the-village",
