        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Centra Midtown 3601 N Central Ave Phoenix, AZ 85012 A wonderful home in Phoenix is waiting for you! Call or text for details at show contact info We currently have a gorgeous 1 bedroom 1 bathroom with 890 sq ft. Monthly Price: $1816 - $2097 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Get ready to raise your vibe and embark on a new chapter of your life at Centra Midtown Phoenix, a brand-new, modern apartment community in Midtown Phoenix. Be in the center of it all with easy access to the arts district, instant light rail access, convenient public transportation, popular eateries and bars, and great shopping. The perfect pet-friendly home is waiting for you and your furry friends, too! This modern community offers accessible Midtown residences that delight with uptown service and arts district vibrancy. Revel in your new modern studio, one- or two-bedroom apartment, designed with cool, contemporary finishes that compliments your active lifestyle. Discover how much of an impact a well-located apartment community can make in your life and take advantage of Centra Midtown Phoenix's convenient location in Midtown Phoenix. Get in now to select your new home before the secret is out and hits the Midtown streets. We are now accepting reservations for our first, awesome Centra Midtown Phoenix residents. Reach out today and stay in the loop on construction progress and leasing updates. It's time to revel in the possibilities at Centra Midtown Phoenix and Raise Your Vibe! Community Highlights: ➢ Barbecue pavilion, mini-golf, and outdoor fire pit ➢ Dog run- we welcome furry friends! ➢ Pet friendly (breed restrictions apply) ➢ Relaxing resort-style pool with sundeck cabanas and spa ➢ Resident social lounge and game room with demonstration kitchen, billiards table, shuffleboard table, and arcade games ➢ Rooftop lounge with panoramic city views ➢ State-of-the-art fitness center with yoga, spin, and cross-fit rooms ➢ Underground gated parking garage with direct access elevators ➢ Built to LEED® Certification ➢ Homes Wi-Fi ready with pre-installed modem/router and first month free provided by Cox ➢ Package locker with 24/7 access to packages ➢ Seconds the from Light Rail station ➢ Virtual moving concierge - Complimentary address change, set up home services and digital moving announcements ➢ Waived App and Admin Fees for Veterans, First Responders, Teachers, and Creighton University students, Pending Application Approval ➢ Walk Score 74 and Bike Score 74 Apartment Home Highlights: ➢ Air conditioning with programmable thermostat ➢ French doors leading to a private balcony or patio ➢ Full size in-home washer and dryer ➢ Furnished apartments available ➢ Kitchen island with pendant lighting ➢ Luxury kitchen tile backsplash ➢ Polished granite countertops ➢ Stainless steel appliances including built-in microwave, refrigerator, gas range, and dishwasher ➢ Wood-style plank flooring in kitchen and living areas ➢ 2-inch faux wood blinds ➢ Ceiling fans in living areas and bedrooms ➢ Deep soaker style bathtubs ➢ Elevator access ➢ Keyless smart lock technology ➢ Oversized walk-in closets ➢ Separate shower with glass enclosure Call or text for details at show contact info Website: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=centra_midtown&rp=tvcgssUot5YB&t=wb Online Application: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=centra_midtown&rp=tvcgssUot5YB&t=ap 3D Virtual Tour: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=centra_midtown&rp=tvcgssUot5YB&t=trt Leasing Options: 3-Month, 4-Month, 5-Month, 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month, 13-Month, 14-Month, 15-Month Pet Policy: Dogs and cats are welcome at our community. All pet residents must have their health check, shots and be spayed or neutered upon move-in. A signed Animal Addendum is required to be on file at our leasing office. Two (2) max pets allowed. Breed restrictions apply. We only rent our apartments directly through our website or leasing office. We do not use any electronic funds transferring apps such as Zelle, Venmo, or Cashapp. All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 798329CBD05A4AB",
