        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post 2150 Apartments Visit Our Community Today! 2150 S Arizona Ave Chandler, AZ 85286 Call us today at show contact info Focused on the well-being of its residents, 2150 Apartments provides a variety of amenities, including a sparkling pool and state-of-the-art fitness center, available to tenants living in one of our 1, 2, or 3 bedroom floor plans. Combine all of this with an ideal location near all Chandler has to offer, and it is clear why our apartment homes are a top location. Come visit us today for your personal tour, where you can truly live your way. Up to 8 weeks FREE when you lease select homes by 6/30/26!* *RESTRICTIONS APPLY. CONTACT US FOR DETAILS. Bedrooms: 2 | Bathrooms: 2 Square Footage: 1067 sq ft Monthly Price: $1564 - $2184 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Our Residents Enjoy: ❖ Barbecue pavilion and picnic area ❖ Basketball court ❖ Controlled-entry access ❖ Dedicated covered parking available ❖ Easy access to Loop 202 ❖ Fenced dog park with pet watering station ❖ Onsite playground ❖ State-of-the-art fitness center ❖ Homes Wi-Fi ready with pre-installed modem/router and first month free provided by Cox ❖ Package locker with 24/7 access to packages ❖ Relaxing resort-style pool with sundeck and spa ❖ Resident social lounge with demonstration kitchen and media room ❖ Virtual moving concierge - Complimentary address change, set up home services and digital moving announcements ❖ Waived App and Admin Fees for Veterans, First Responders and Teachers. This Apartment Home Comes With: ❖ 9-foot ceilings ❖ In-home washer and dryer ❖ Kitchen breakfast bar ❖ Oversized walk-in closets ❖ Private balcony or patio ❖ Air conditioning with programmable thermostat ❖ Furnished apartments available ❖ Polished quartz and granite countertops ❖ Stainless steel appliances including built-in microwave, refrigerator, and dishwasher ❖ Wood-style plank flooring Website: www.apts-rental.com?n=2150&rp=ti6Diuoe7FTA&t=wb Online Application: www.apts-rental.com?n=2150&rp=ti6Diuoe7FTA&t=ap 3D Virtual Tour: www.apts-rental.com?n=2150&rp=ti6Diuoe7FTA&t=trt Call us today at show contact info Pet-Policy: Dogs and cats are welcome at our community. All pet residents must have their health check, shots and be spayed or neutered upon move-in. A signed Animal Addendum is required to be on file at our leasing office. Two (2) max pets allowed. Lease-Length: 3-Month, 4-Month, 5-Month, 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month, 13-Month, 14-Month Call for Directions We only rent our apartments directly through our website or leasing office. We do not use any electronic funds transferring apps such as Zelle, Venmo, or Cashapp. All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 5C8BD5120A01436",
