        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post The Glendale Address: 6819 N 27th Ave Phoenix, AZ 85017 Monthly Price: $974 - $1189 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Bedrooms: 1 | Baths: 1 | Sq. Footage: 600 sq ft | Terms: 12-Month Call us today! show contact info Starting at $974 + Receive First Month FREE Celebrate our Grand Opening and reserve your new home today! Limited availability - call or apply today. *Prices and specials are subject to change, valid on approved applications upon move-in. Select floor plans, lease terms, or restrictions may apply. Contact the leasing office for more details. + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + Features in this apartment home: ➢ Ceiling Fan ➢ Dishwasher ➢ Disposal ➢ High Ceilings ➢ Microwave ➢ Refrigerator ➢ Air Conditioner ➢ Full Size Stove ➢ Large Closets ➢ Plank Wood-Style Flooring ➢ Spacious Kitchen ➢ Window Coverings + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + Amenities at our property: ➢ Community Center ➢ Courtyard ➢ Covered Parking ➢ Dog Park ➢ EV Charging Station ➢ Fitness Center ➢ Laundry Facilities ➢ Lever style door knobs ➢ Microwave on counter ➢ Walking Path ➢ Convenient Connections to Downtown Phoenix, Shopping, and Services ➢ High Speed Internet ➢ Membership to Helen Drake Senior Center ➢ On-Site Maintenance ➢ On-Site Management + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + About the community: 55+ Senior Apartments Coming April 2026! Discover affordable 1-bedroom senior apartments designed for comfort and convenience in the heart of Phoenix. The Glendale offers easy access to everyday essentials with a bus stop for the Valley Metro Route 27 right next door and quick connections via N 27th Avenue and I-17 to downtown Phoenix and beyond. Pets: Pets - allowed Rent $10.00, Deposit $200.00, Call us today! show contact info Hours: Mon - Fri: 9:00 AM - 5:00 PM Website: www.apt-rental.com?n=glendale&rp=fagNnx1UHsNH&t=wb Online Application: www.apt-rental.com?n=glendale&rp=fagNnx1UHsNH&t=ap Please be advised that our community is operated under Section 42 of the Internal Revenue Code. This is a special Financing program designed to facilitate the housing needs of moderate and middle-income households. Residency at this community requires that applicants meet certain qualifying standards established by the government. This program is not connected with Section 8; however, we do accept Section 8 participants. Residency at this community is limited to those households moderate incomes as noted in this county. Fees: Application fee is $35 per adult. * Pricing and availability are subject to change. ** SQFT listed is an approximate value for each unit. All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 090JO6SV0X50AT",
