        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Scottsdale Horizon Apartments Featured Floorplan: 1-bed / 1-bath / 765 sq ft Monthly Price: $1464 - $1736 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Deposit: Call Reach out via phone or text: show contact info Description: A 24-hour state-of-the-art fitness center is always there to help you stay in shape, while the Wi-Fi Cafe and business center make sure you're always on top of your game. Inside your new home, fine details and thoughtful features await. You'll love the private balconies or patios that come with each of our 1 and 2 bedroom apartments, as well as our plush carpeting, wood-style flooring, efficient appliances, and inspired layouts. Plus, we also offer full-size washer and dryers, assigned covered parking for all our residents, and a professional staff dedicated to making your apartment living experience at Scottsdale Horizon unforgettable. Up to 4 weeks FREE when you move in by 7/15/26 on select lease terms!* *RESTRICTIONS APPLY. CONTACT US FOR DETAILS. Lease Terms: 3-Month, 4-Month, 5-Month, 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month, 13-Month, 14-Month, 15-Month Pet Policy: We welcome you and your pet to your new home. Before moving in, please take a moment to review our pet policy. Apartment Amenities: ➢ Furnished apartments available ➢ In-home washer and dryer ➢ Polished granite countertops ➢ Wheelchair Access in Select Units ➢ Wood-style flooring ➢ Energy-efficient appliances including built-in microwave, refrigerator, and dishwasher ➢ Mosaic tile kitchen backsplash ➢ Private balcony or patio ➢ Wheelchair Access in Select Units Community Features: ➢ 24-hour fitness center with free weights and cardio machines ➢ Barbecue pavilion and picnic area ➢ Co-working lounge with complimentary Wi-Fi ➢ Package locker with 24/7 access to packages ➢ Reserved covered parking ➢ Resident social lounge ➢ Two resort-style pools with sundeck and spas ➢ Homes Wi-Fi ready with pre-installed modem/router and first month free provided by Cox ➢ Lush landscaped grounds ➢ Putting green ➢ Virtual Moving Concierge: Complimentary address change, set up home services and digital moving announcements ➢ Waived App and Admin Fees for Veterans, First Responders and Teachers. Address: 9259 E Raintree Dr Scottsdale, AZ 85260 Reach out via phone or text: show contact info Mon - Tue: 9:00 AM - 6:00 PM Wed: 12:00 PM - 6:00 PM Thu - Fri: 9:00 AM - 6:00 PM Sat - Sun: 10:00 AM - 5:00 PM Website: www.apts-rental.com?n=scottsdale_horizon&rp=9ZSAQ32eRZrg&t=wb Online Application: www.apts-rental.com?n=scottsdale_horizon&rp=9ZSAQ32eRZrg&t=ap 3D Virtual Tour: www.apts-rental.com?n=scottsdale_horizon&rp=9ZSAQ32eRZrg&t=trt We only rent our apartments directly through our website or leasing office. We do not use any electronic funds transferring apps such as Zelle, Venmo, or Cashapp. All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY ACC983C26D4A4437",
