        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post Natura Villas Apartment Homes 10847 W Olive Ave Peoria, AZ 85345 Monthly Price: $1195 - $1650 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Bedrooms: 1 Bathrooms: 1 Square Footage: 740 sq ft Contact Info: show contact info Features in this apartment home: ✓ Accent Walls Available ✓ Black on Black Whirlpool Appliances ✓ Ceiling Fan(s) ✓ Garden Tubs Available ✓ Granite-like Counter-tops ✓ Large Patios ✓ New/Renovated Interior ✓ Oversize Walk-in Closets ✓ Replicated Wood Flooring ✓ Washer/Dryer in Every Home About the community: From the moment you step on the property, lush landscaping and expansive greenbelts stretch in every direction. The signature Great Room's floor-to-ceiling glass doors that open to seamlessly connect the interior with the expansive outdoor covered patio complete with a large fireplace lounge area. The Great room also welcomes you with a complimentary coffee bar, free wifi, flat-screen TVs, and plush seating throughout. For the fitness enthusiast, Natura Villas is equipped with a state-of-the-art 24 hour fitness center and a corn hole court. Residents will enjoy a dedicated Pet Park with agility equipment and two resort style pools and spas. It's easy to see why Natura Villas is setting a new standard for luxury residential living in the Northwest Valley! Amenities at our property: ✓ Billiards Table ✓ Business Center ✓ Corn Hole ✓ Extra Storage ✓ Fitness Center ✓ Freeway Access ✓ Gas Barbecues ✓ Gated Community ✓ Luxury Community ✓ Playground ✓ 2 Resort Inspired Pools & Spas ✓ 24-Hour Emergency Maintenance ✓ Detached Garages Available ✓ Online Maintenance Requests ✓ Online Rent Payment ✓ Outdoor Lounge with Stainless Steel Barbeques ✓ Pet Friendly ✓ Pet Park with Agility Equipment ✓ Public Transportation ✓ Wi-Fi and Coffee Bar Additional information: Contact Info: show contact info Terms: 3-Month, 4-Month, 5-Month, 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month, 13-Month, 14-Month, 15-Month Pets: No Weight Restrictions 2 pets per apartment home $300 per pet deposit $45 pet rent $300 non-refundable pet fee Pet must be less than 25\" from hind down Breed restrictions apply Website: www.rentalsapts.com?n=natura_villas&rp=tkcYwvcodawV&t=wb Online Application: www.rentalsapts.com?n=natura_villas&rp=tkcYwvcodawV&t=ap 3D Virtual Tour: www.rentalsapts.com?n=natura_villas&rp=tkcYwvcodawV&t=trt All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 3DEE9691854146C",
