        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post Welcome to Andante Apartments Rental Information Monthly Price: $1746 - $2419 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. 2 Bedroom 2 Bath | 1212 sq ft Lease Term: 3-Month, 4-Month, 5-Month, 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month, 13-Month, 14-Month, 15-Month Call or text us today at show contact info Up to 1 month FREE!* *RESTRICTIONS APPLY. CONTACT US FOR DETAILS. Apartment Amenities − 9-foot ceilings − Air conditioning with programmable thermostat − French doors leading to private patio − Furnished apartments available − In-home washer and dryer − Oversized walk-in closets − Polished quartz countertops − Stainless steel appliances including built-in microwave, refrigerator, and dishwasher − Subway tile kitchen backsplash − 2-inch faux wood blinds − Ceiling fans in living areas and bedrooms − Deep soaker style bathtubs Community Features − Barbecue pavilion and picnic area − Controlled-entry access − Co-working lounge with complimentary Wi-Fi − Dog wash and self-service grooming area − Indoor/outdoor resident social lounge with demonstration kitchen and billiards table and foosball − Large and small breed fenced dog parks with pet watering station − Private attached garages available and reserved covered parking − Relaxing resort-style pool with sundeck and spa − State-of-the-art fitness center − Built to Green Globes Building Certification − Easy access to I-10, Loop 101, and Loop 202 − Homes Wi-Fi ready with pre-installed modem/router and first month free provided by Cox − Landscaped courtyard with outdoor seating − Package locker with 24/7 access to packages − Virtual Moving Concierge: Complimentary address change, set up home services and digital moving announcements − Waived App and Admin Fees for Veterans, First Responders and Teachers − Worry-free 24-hour onsite maintenance About Community Description: For those looking for a high standard of excellence from apartment living, Andante Apartments is a perfect choice. Our luxury apartments for rent in Phoenix, AZ provide a five-star living experience comparable to what you might find at a getaway resort! Imagine living in a relaxing and laid back resort-style atmosphere, but for the long term. The elegance and design of our one and two bedroom apartment homes are sure to impress. Take a look at our multiple floor plan options to find the home that best suits your taste and layout preference. We know that having options is important, which is why we provide several high-quality floor plans to choose from. It doesn't end there though, each of our apartment homes comes complete with top-notch features and amenities that extend beyond the walls of your new home! As you walk into your new apartment home for the first time, you will fall in love with the large bay windows, 9 foot ceilings, modern stainless steel appliances, and gorgeous French doors that lead to your very own private patio. Beyond your home, you'll discover satisfying community amenities like our gorgeous swimming pool and hot tub, outdoor grills, a fitness center with free weights, and much more! Enjoy several options when it comes to parking. Our community features open parking, as well as carports and attached garages so finding parking will never be an issue. Our apartment community is also pet-friendly with no weight limit! We welcome cats and dogs and the positive impact they have on the happiness and health of our residents. Our ideal location in South Phoenix provides access to premium shopping, dining, and entertainment options. You'll have easy access to I-10, as well as Loop 101 and Loop 202. Enjoy nearby local attractions like the Pecos Community Center and the South Mountain Hiking Trails. You'll be able to have it all when you live here at Andante Apartments! Give us a call to schedule a tour of your new home. Location: 15801 S 48th St Phoenix, AZ 85048 show contact info Office Hours: Mon - Tue: 9:00 AM - 6:00 PM Wed: 12:00 PM - 6:00 PM Thu - Fri: 9:00 AM - 6:00 PM Sat - Sun: 10:00 AM - 5:00 PM Additional Information Call or text us today at show contact info Pet Policy: Dogs and cats are welcome at our community. All pet residents must have their health check, shots and be spayed or neutered upon move-in. A signed Animal Addendum is required to be on file at our leasing office. Two (2) max pets allowed. Breed restrictions apply. Website: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=andante&rp=mChcTjVkwZgL&t=wb Online Application: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=andante&rp=mChcTjVkwZgL&t=ap 3D Virtual Tour: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=andante&rp=mChcTjVkwZgL&t=trt We only rent our apartments directly through our website or leasing office. We do not use any electronic funds transferring apps such as Zelle, Venmo, or Cashapp. All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY A876E646149848",
