        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post Welcome to IMT Riverview! 711 N Evergreen Road Mesa, AZ 85201 Call us today at show contact info Rental Size: 2 BR - 2 BA - 1132 sq ft Monthly Price: $1918 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Lease Length: 3-Month, 4-Month, 5-Month, 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month LOOK & LEASE: Receive 1 month free rent when you apply within 24 hours of your tour.* *Restrictions apply; offer subject to change at any time. Offer expires on 06/29/26. Special offer only applies to base rent and not any fees included in Total Monthly Price. Credit will apply to the second full month’s statement. Special excludes all property transfers and current residents. 12-month minimum lease term applies. **Walk-ins welcome & choose from 3 tour options.** A community feeling is what you get at IMT Riverview's Mesa, AZ apartments. Relax outdoors in style at the resort-style pool and spa featuring luxurious seating and draped cabanas and a fireside lounge area, or enjoy a fun filled day of outdoor dining at the convenient picnic and barbeque areas. Or enjoy an invigorating workout in the fully-equipped fitness center. If you need to get some work done and need a computer or a conference room, we've got you covered. All this and an apartment full of conveniences, from a washer and dryer to your large walk in closet, you're going to love coming home. Take a Virtual Tour of Our Property Today! https://liveimt.com/imtRiverviewYoutubeTour Price shown is Total Monthly Price including monthly mandatory fees* Mandatory Fees: - Package Locker: $5/month - Credit Reporting: $5/month - Service Fee: $3/month - Sewer Charge: Varies - Trash: Varies - Water Charges: Varies Our community features: ◾ Assigned Parking ◾ BBQ Area ◾ Business Center ◾ Coffee Bar ◾ Fitness Center ◾ Freeway Access ◾ On-Line Payments ◾ Pet Friendly ◾ Public Transportation ◾ Shopping Nearby ◾ Apache Light Rail Station one mile ◾ Conference Room & High-Tech Business Center ◾ Convenient freeway access to the 101 and 202 ◾ Fireside lounge ◾ Minutes from Sky Harbor Airport and downtown Phoenix ◾ Near Tempe Market Place and Mesa Riverview ◾ Private garages or covered parking available ◾ Resort-style aquamarine pool and spa ◾ Shaded conversation lanais and lush green courtyards ◾ Spacious outdoor entertainment space with beautiful picnic areas Our apartment features: ◾ Built-in Bookshelves In Select Homes ◾ Built-in Linen Closets In Select Homes ◾ Ceiling Fans ◾ Ceramic Tile Flooring In Select Homes ◾ Decorative Crown Molding ◾ Fully Equipped Kitchens, Including Microwave & Ref ◾ High-efficiency Central Air ◾ Large Walk-in Closets ◾ Personal Storage Space In Select Homes ◾ Spacious Private Patio or Balcony Call us today at -- show contact info -- Our Pet-Policy: At IMT Riverview, we know that the path to your heart is marked with paw prints and that the best part of your day is coming home to a wagging tail. Pets are residents too! Pets Welcome! Two pets maximum $300 Pet Fee/$30 monthly Pet Rent per pet No weight limit. Breed restrictions apply. Website: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=imt_riverview&rp=kCsmwgu9q2Zf&t=wb *Total Monthly Price includes base rent, all monthly mandatory and any user-selected optional fees. Excludes variable, usage-based, and required charges due at or prior to move-in or at move-out. Discounts, if applicable, will be calculated upon lease execution. Minimum lease terms and occupancy guidelines may apply. Deposits may vary based on credit, rental history, income, or other qualifying criteria. Additional fees and taxes may apply and will be disclosed per governing laws and company policies. Total Monthly Price may be displayed as a whole dollar amount for advertising purposes only; actual charges are calculated using exact fee amounts, including cents, and may vary from the displayed amount by up to 50 cents due to rounding. Mandatory Fees: - Package Locker: $5/month - Credit Reporting: $5/month - Service Fee: $3/month - Sewer Charge: Varies - Trash: Varies - Water Charges: Varies All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 722E172FE4444A2",
