        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Welcome home to NOVO Broadway! Located at: 711 West Broadway Road Tempe, AZ 85282 Rental Information: # of Bedrooms: 2 # of Bathrooms: 2 Square Footage: 1060 sq ft Monthly Price: $1969 - $2520 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Call for details: show contact info Our community is set apart from others, with our resort-style pool, outdoor firepit lounge area, and stunning Camelback Mountain views just waiting to welcome you home. Enjoy the conveniences and flexibility of an active lifestyle with our 24-hour fitness center, pamper your furry friend with our on-site dog park and dog wash station, or put in some work time at the communal co-working lounge. Enjoy a virtual tour and then come and see what vibrant and beautiful Tempe living looks like at NOVO Broadway. Up to 8 weeks free when you apply by 6/24/2026!* *RESTRICTIONS APPLY. CONTACT US FOR DETAILS. Community Features: ◾ Barbecue pavilion ◾ Camelback Mountain views ◾ Controlled-entry access ◾ Co-working lounge ◾ Dog park and pet wash station ◾ Easy freeway access ◾ Elevator access ◾ EV car charging stations ◾ Outdoor fire pit lounge area ◾ Reserved covered parking ◾ 24-hour fitness center with free weights and cardio machines ◾ Indoor mailroom with Amazon parcel lockers ◾ Move-in with NO SECURITY DEPOSIT: Only a small one-time payment ◾ Relaxing resort-style pool with sundeck and spa ◾ Resident social lounge with TV and coffee bar ◾ Virtual moving concierge - Complimentary address change, set up home services and digital moving announcements Apartment Home Features: ◾ 9-14 foot ceilings ◾ Air conditioning ◾ Dual-pane windows ◾ Oversized closets ◾ Private patio or balcony ◾ Stainless steel appliances ◾ USB charging ports ◾ Ceiling fans with integrated lighting ◾ Furnished apartments available ◾ Gourmet kitchens with granite countertops ◾ In-home washer and dryer ◾ Luxurious bathrooms with high-end finishes ◾ Wood-style plank flooring with carpet in bedrooms Office Hours: Mon - Fri: 9:00 AM - 6:00 PM Sat - Sun: 10:00 AM - 5:00 PM Call for details: show contact info Pet Policy: We welcome you and your pet to your new home. Before moving in, please take a moment to review our pet policy. Leasing Options: 3-Month, 4-Month, 5-Month, 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month, 13-Month Website: www.lease-apts.com?n=novo_broadway&rp=iE4wYTSu68Co&t=wb Online Application: www.lease-apts.com?n=novo_broadway&rp=iE4wYTSu68Co&t=ap 3D Virtual Tour: www.lease-apts.com?n=novo_broadway&rp=iE4wYTSu68Co&t=trt Schedule a Tour: www.lease-apts.com?n=novo_broadway&rp=iE4wYTSu68Co&t=sch We only rent our apartments directly through our website or leasing office. We do not use any electronic funds transferring apps such as Zelle, Venmo, or Cashapp. All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY F279382775374F1",
