        "mainpic": "2a82e37d-a0db-40fb-a29c-5fbcf6be0a20",
        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post Sonoran Apartment Homes Visit Our Community Today! 13625 S 48th St Phoenix, AZ 85044 Drop us a call or text at show contact info Each of our apartment homes comes with a fully equipped kitchen that includes a dishwasher and a garbage disposal to help clean up. The apartment also comes with an oversized closet to store your personal belongings, as well as a washer and dryer to help tackle laundry day. After you have settled into one of the apartments, you can enjoy a plethora of amenities right outside your door. Sonoran is located within an Ahwatukee gated community that includes covered parking and a courtesy officer. The pet-friendly community has nearby trails for biking, hiking, and jogging. We have a beautifully styled pool that is available for a refreshing dip whenever you might need a refreshment. The pool deck also includes a spa, the perfect place to unwind after a long day. A barbecue and picnic area are located a few feet away from the pool with plenty of room to meet with neighbors. The outdoor area also includes a volleyball court for a rousing game with neighbors. Sonoran also offers plenty of indoor community amenities for you to enjoy, including a state-of-the-art fitness center with modern exercise equipment. Stop by Sonoran today to find out more about these luxury amenities exclusive to this community! Best Rate in Town Up to 4 weeks FREE when you move in by 7/15/26 on select lease terms!* *RESTRICTIONS APPLY. CONTACT US FOR DETAILS. Bedrooms: 3 | Bathrooms: 2 Square Footage: 1204 sq ft Monthly Price: $1900 - $2859 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Our Residents Enjoy: − Barbecue pavilion and picnic area − Courtesy patrol − Event courtyard − Heated resort-style pool with sundeck and spa − Pet friendly (breed restrictions apply) − Reserved covered parking − Smoke-free community − State-of-the-art fitness center − Steps from Valley Metro Bus stop − Flexible lease terms available − Homes Wi-Fi ready with pre-installed modem/router and first month free provided by Cox − Professional onsite management − Virtual Moving Concierge: Complimentary address change, set up home services and digital moving announcements − Waived App and Admin Fees for Veterans, First Responders and Teachers. − Worry-free 24-hour onsite maintenance This Apartment Home Comes With: − Air conditioning with programmable thermostat − Furnished apartments available − In-home washer and dryer − Polished quartz countertops − Private balcony or patio − Stainless steel appliances including built-in microwave, refrigerator, and dishwasher − Subway tile kitchen backsplash − White shaker cabinetry − 2-inch faux wood blinds − Built-in linen closet − Ceiling fans in living areas and bedrooms − Cozy wood fireplaces available − Oversized walk-in closets − Separate dining area − Wood-style plank flooring Website: www.apt-rental.com?n=sonoran&rp=8t7sVTD6GBA8&t=wb Online Application: www.apt-rental.com?n=sonoran&rp=8t7sVTD6GBA8&t=ap 3D Virtual Tour: www.apt-rental.com?n=sonoran&rp=8t7sVTD6GBA8&t=trt Drop us a call or text at show contact info Pet-Policy: Dogs and cats are welcome at our community. All pet residents must have their health check, shots and be spayed or neutered upon move-in. A signed Animal Addendum is required to be on file at our leasing office. Two (2) max pets allowed. Breed restrictions apply. Lease-Length: 3-Month, 4-Month, 5-Month, 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month, 13-Month Call for Directions We only rent our apartments directly through our website or leasing office. We do not use any electronic funds transferring apps such as Zelle, Venmo, or Cashapp. All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 3B6F5CF248DD4FF9",
