        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post IMT Ahwatukee Leasing Office: 5010 E Cheyenne Dr Phoenix, AZ 85044 Contact us for more information! show contact info Take a look at what IMT Ahwatukee has to offer! IMT Ahwatukee apartments in Phoenix features luxury one, two, and three bedroom apartments homes with seven different floorplans to choose from. These pet-friendly homes come with everything you need to live comfortably from fully-equipped kitchens and in-home washers & dryers to private balconies or patios. Explore a home that you deserve. Take a Virtual Tour of Our Property Today! https://viewer.panoskin.com?tour=628fd0d65880ba7559ed98f8 Please copy and paste to take a video tour: https://liveimt.com/imtAhwatukeeYoutubeTour Price shown is Total Monthly Price including monthly mandatory fees* Monthly Mandatory Fees: - Package Locker: $5/month - Credit Reporting: $5/month - Service Fee: $4.25/month - Water Charge: Varies - Sewer Charge: Varies - Pest: $2.30/Month - Valet Trash Service: $25/month - Flood control: Varies - Central AZ Water Conservation: Varies - Common Area Electric: Varies - Common Area Gas: Varies LOOK & LEASE: Receive 1 month free rent when you apply within 24 hours of your tour.* *Restrictions apply; offer subject to change at any time. Offer expires on 06/29/26. Special offer only applies to base rent and not any fees included in Total Monthly Price. Credit will apply to the second full month's statement. Special excludes all property transfers and current residents. 12-month minimum lease term applies. Rental Information: 2 Bedroom / 2 Bathroom / 1050 sq ft Monthly Price: $1852 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Lease Terms: Variable Apartment Amenities: ✓ Bay Windows In Select Homes ✓ Cable & Satellite TV Available ✓ Ceiling Fans with Light Kits ✓ Fireplaces In Select Homes ✓ Fully Equipped Kitchens with Stainless Steel Appliances ✓ High-Speed Internet Access ✓ Linen Closets ✓ Nine Foot Ceilings In Select Homes ✓ Private Balconies or Patios ✓ Vaulted Ceilings In Select Homes Additional Information: ✓ Clubhouse ✓ IMT Active ✓ IMT Pets Park ✓ Outdoor Ramada ✓ Pickleball Court ✓ Table Tennis ✓ Tennis Court ✓ Two Outdoor Picnic Areas with Barbecue Grills ✓ Two Swimming Pools & Spas ✓ 24/7 Emergency Maintenance Service ✓ 24-Hour Package Lockers ✓ Corn Hole ✓ Covered & Reserved Parking Available ✓ Detached Garages Available ✓ My IMT Resident Portal with Online & On-Site Kiosk Access: Utilities Connection, Rent Payment, Service Requests, Amenity Reservations, Account Information & Community Postings ✓ Playground ✓ Storage Available Leasing Hours: Mon - Fri: 8:30 AM - 5:30 PM Sat: 10:00 AM - 5:00 PM Sun: - Contact us for more information! show contact info Pet Policy: At IMT Ahwatukee, we know that the path to your heart is marked with paw prints and that the best part of your day is coming home to a wagging tail. Pets are residents too! TWO PET MAXIMUM NO WEIGHT RESTRICTIONS, BREED RESTRICTIONS APPLY $250 REFUNDABLE PET DEPOSIT, PER PET $250 NON-REFUNDABLE PET FEE, PER PET $40 PET RENT, PER PET Website: www.apts-rental.com?n=imt_ahwatukee&rp=sEL5ZhgKtvbs&t=wb *Total Monthly Price includes base rent, all monthly mandatory and any user-selected optional fees. Excludes variable, usage-based, and required charges due at or prior to move-in or at move-out. Discounts, if applicable, will be calculated upon lease execution. Minimum lease terms and occupancy guidelines may apply. Deposits may vary based on credit, rental history, income, or other qualifying criteria. Additional fees and taxes may apply and will be disclosed per governing laws and company policies. Total Monthly Price may be displayed as a whole dollar amount for advertising purposes only; actual charges are calculated using exact fee amounts, including cents, and may vary from the displayed amount by up to 50 cents due to rounding. Price shown is Total Monthly Price including monthly mandatory fees* Monthly Mandatory Fees: - Package Locker: $5/month - Credit Reporting: $5/month - Service Fee: $4.25/month - Water Charge: Varies - Sewer Charge: Varies - Pest: $2.30/Month - Valet Trash Service: $25/month - Flood control: Varies - Central AZ Water Conservation: Varies - Common Area Electric: Varies - Common Area Gas: Varies All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY A2D469E17EEC4E8",
