        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post RENTAL INFO Monthly Price: $1226 - $1370 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. The Retreat Apartments: 20808 N 27th Ave Phoenix, AZ 85027 Apartment for Rent: 1-BR 1-BA | Square Feet: 725 sq ft | Lease Length: 3-Month, 4-Month, 5-Month, 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month, 13-Month Call for details: show contact info PROPERTY AMENITIES ◾ Barbecue pavilion ◾ Dedicated parking ◾ Easy access to I-17 and the 101 ◾ Fenced dog park ◾ Fire pit ◾ Garages available ◾ Onsite playground ◾ Pet friendly (breed restrictions apply) ◾ Poolside terrace featuring ◾ State-of-the-art fitness center ◾ Eco-friendly community features onsite recycling ◾ Homes Wi-Fi ready with pre-installed modem/router and first month free provided by Cox ◾ Multiple relaxing resort-style pools and sundecks ◾ Onsite and offsite resident programs tailored to our community ◾ Resident social lounge with demonstration kitchen and billiards table ◾ Virtual Moving Concierge: Complimentary address change, set up home services and digital moving announcements ◾ Waived App and Admin Fees for Veterans, First Responders and Teachers. APARTMENT AMENITIES ◾ 9-foot ceilings ◾ Air conditioning ◾ Built-in microwave ◾ Dishwasher ◾ Fireplaces available ◾ In-home washer and dryer ◾ Private balcony or patio ◾ Programmable thermostat ◾ Refrigerator ◾ Stainless steel appliances ◾ 2-inch faux wood blinds ◾ Ceiling fans in living areas and bedrooms ◾ Furnished apartments available ◾ Oversized walk-in closets ◾ Separate dining area ◾ Two-tone paint ◾ USB charging outlets ◾ Wood-style plank flooring in kitchen and living areas ADDITIONAL INFO Description: The Retreat Apartments is your everyday oasis ideally located on a stunning Sonoran landscape in the Deer Valley area of North Phoenix. Our 1, 2 & 3 bedroom apartments feature gorgeous spaces designed for high-end style and comfort. Modern finishes are sleek and chic throughout the home, while energy-efficient appliances and an in-home washer and dryer effortlessly keep chores under control. Pet Policy: PET POLICY OVERVIEW Dogs and cats are welcome at our community. All pet residents must have their health check, shots and be spayed or neutered upon move-in. A signed Animal Addendum is required to be on file at our leasing office. Two (2) max pets allowed. Website: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=retreat&rp=uUsYA85DJTS6&t=wb Online Application: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=retreat&rp=uUsYA85DJTS6&t=ap 3D Virtual Tour: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=retreat&rp=uUsYA85DJTS6&t=trt Call for details: show contact info We only rent our apartments directly through our website or leasing office. We do not use any electronic funds transferring apps such as Zelle, Venmo, or Cashapp. All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY AA73FB871249410",
