        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Elevate at Discovery Park 1820 E Bell De Mar Dr Tempe, AZ 85283 Call or text us today at show contact info . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . Rental Size: 1 BR - 1 BA - 704 sq ft Monthly Price: $1541 - $1758 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Lease Length: 3-Month, 4-Month, 5-Month, 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month, 13-Month, 14-Month, 15-Month, 16-Month . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . Style meets sophistication at Elevate at Discovery Park, offering a heightened living experience with modern spaces and beautiful surroundings. Our apartment homes are uniquely designed with authentic architecture and intricate designs that provide a Spanish-style feel and deliver gorgeous, upgraded interiors, and resort-style community amenities. . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . Features and Amenities: ● 24-hour fitness center with free weights and cardio machines ● Fenced dog park with pet watering station ● On-site professional management team ● Relaxing resort-style pool with sundeck and spa ● Reserved covered parking ● Terrace featuring fire pit, barbecue pavilion, and picnic area ● Walking distance to dining, shopping, and nightlife ● Worry-free 24-hour onsite maintenance ● Easy access to public transportation ● Easy access to U.S. 60, Loop 101, and I-10 Freeway Systems ● Flexible lease terms available ● Homes Wi-Fi ready with pre-installed modem/router and first month free provided by Cox ● Less than 5 miles from Arizona State University ● Onsite access to Tempe Stroud Park ● Pet friendly (breed restrictions apply) . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . This Apartment Home Comes With: ● Air conditioning with programmable thermostat ● Energy-efficient appliances including built-in microwave, refrigerator, and dishwasher ● In-home washer and dryer ● Oversized walk-in closets ● Polished granite kitchen countertops ● Private balcony or patio ● Separate dining area ● Wood-style plank flooring ● Ceiling fans in living areas and bedrooms ● Courtyard and pool views ● Fireplaces available ● Vaulted ceilings . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . Call or text us today at -- show contact info -- Website: www.apt-rental.com?n=elevate_at_discovery_park&rp=6r22SrUwQ2S4&t=wb Online Application: www.apt-rental.com?n=elevate_at_discovery_park&rp=6r22SrUwQ2S4&t=ap Pets: Dogs and cats are welcome at our community. All pet residents must have their health check, shots and be spayed or neutered upon move-in. A signed Animal Addendum is required to be on file at our leasing office. Two (2) max pets allowed. . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . We only rent our apartments directly through our website or leasing office. We do not use any electronic funds transferring apps such as Zelle, Venmo, or Cashapp. All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY F1C627A071BB41",
