        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Welcome to Budget Suites where you can make one of our apartments your home for a week or beyond! Our properties are designed to serve you with amenities including all essential utilities paid, full sized kitchens & appliances, pools and spas, laundry facilities with 24/7 courtesy patrol, high speed internet, Cox cable television with premium channels including HBO and ESPN, and much more! We are pet friendly as well! Budget Suites has the convenience of a hotel, with all the comforts of home. We welcome you to your new home!! Our famous budget prices include: • Fully Furnished Apartments • All Utilities Paid • Cox Cable TV • Full Size Kitchens • Full Size Appliances • On-Site Laundry Facilities • Covered Parking Available • Beautiful Pools and Spas • Onsite Maintenance • Onsite Property Management • 24/7 Courtesy Patrol Available upgrades to your apartment include: • Deluxe Flooring • WiFi • Flat Screen HD TV • Microwave Weekly rates START as low as $279 base rate for our 1 bedrooms (+taxes and fees), deposit is required at check-in with first payment. Two weeks minimum move in. No credit check is required. No application fee. No lease. Move in on the same day! Criminal Background check is ran upon move in so have a valid state ID/ passport. Budget Suites of America- Come Live A While. Please call show contact info",
