        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post 1 Bedroom 1 Bathroom | 761 sq ft Monthly Price: $1745 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. IMT Desert Ridge 21155 N 56Th St Phoenix, AZ 85054 Contact Info: show contact info Description: Take in the scenery and settle into luxury at IMT Desert Ridge. With a central location near Loop 101 and Piestewa Freeway, our one and two bedroom apartments in North Phoenix, offer up-to-the-minute convenience and best-in-class comfort. The ultramodern Arizona living experience continues alongside the waters of the resort-inspired swimming pool and sleek sundeck lounge. Experience a fresh perspective on distinctive suburban living at our gated community near Desert Ridge Marketplace. Price shown is Total Monthly Price including monthly mandatory fees* Monthly Mandatory Fees: - Package Locker: $5/month - Credit Reporting: $5/month - Amenity Fee: $5/month - Admin Billing Fee: 4/ Month - Sewer Charges: Varies - Valet Trash Service: $25/month - Water Charges: Varies - Pest: $2/month Apartment Amenities: ✓ Ceiling Fans ✓ Custom Cabinetry with Brushed Nickel Hardware ✓ Direct Access Garages* ✓ Fully-Equipped Kitchens including Stainless Steel Appliances and Kitchen Pantries ✓ In-Home Washers and Dryers ✓ Kitchen Islands or Breakfast Bar* ✓ Private Patios and Balconies ✓ Spacious Walk-in Closets ✓ Storage Closets* ✓ Wood-Style Flooring ✓ Custom Cabinetry with Brushed Nickel Hardware ✓ Full-Size Washer & Dryer ✓ Open-Concept Floor Plans ✓ Plank, Wood-Style Flooring ✓ Private Balcony or Patio ✓ Spectacular Desert Views ✓ Stainless Steel Appliances ✓ Upgraded Lighting Fixtures & Ceiling Fans Our Residents Enjoy: ✓ 24-Hour Package Lockers ✓ Accepts Credit Card Payments ✓ BBQ Area ✓ Clubhouse with Kitchen, Billiards, and Ping Pong Table ✓ Common Area Wi-Fi ✓ Direct Access Walking Trails ✓ Gated Access ✓ Outdoor Lounge with Fire Pit, Barbecue Area, and Corn Hole ✓ Poolside Loungers, Cabanas, and Fire Pit ✓ Resort-Style Swimming Pool & Spa Additional Details: Deposit: Call Terms: 3-Month, 4-Month, 5-Month, 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month Pets: At IMT Desert Ridge, we know that the path to your heart is marked with paw prints and that the best part of your day is coming home to a wagging tail. Pets are residents too! Two Pet Maximum - No Weight Restrictions - Breed Restrictions Apply $300 Non-Refundable Pet Fee, Per Pet $35 Pet Rent, Per Pet LOOK & LEASE: Receive 1 month free rent when you apply within 24 hours of your tour.* *Restrictions apply; offer subject to change at any time. Offer expires on 06/29/26. Special offer only applies to base rent and not any fees included in Total Monthly Price. Credit will apply to the second full month’s statement. Special excludes all property transfers and current residents. 12-month minimum lease term applies. Contact Info: show contact info Website: www.apts-rental.com?n=imt_desert_ridge&rp=5qR364RYtz2Y&t=wb 3D Virtual Tour: www.apts-rental.com?n=imt_desert_ridge&rp=5qR364RYtz2Y&t=trt *Total Monthly Price includes base rent, all monthly mandatory and any user-selected optional fees. Excludes variable, usage-based, and required charges due at or prior to move-in or at move-out. Discounts, if applicable, will be calculated upon lease execution. Minimum lease terms and occupancy guidelines may apply. Deposits may vary based on credit, rental history, income, or other qualifying criteria. Additional fees and taxes may apply and will be disclosed per governing laws and company policies. Total Monthly Price may be displayed as a whole dollar amount for advertising purposes only; actual charges are calculated using exact fee amounts, including cents, and may vary from the displayed amount by up to 50 cents due to rounding. Price shown is Total Monthly Price including monthly mandatory fees* Monthly Mandatory Fees: - Package Locker: $5/month - Credit Reporting: $5/month - Amenity Fee: $5/month - Admin Billing Fee: 4/ Month - Sewer Charges: Varies - Valet Trash Service: $25/month - Water Charges: Varies - Pest: $2/month All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY LGXREL1DASL1RSO",
