imit! We welcome cats and dogs and the positive impact they have on the happiness and health of our residents. Our ideal location in South Phoenix provides access to premium shopping, dining, and entertainment options. You'll have easy access to I-10, as well as Loop 101 and Loop 202. Enjoy nearby local attractions like the Pecos Community Center and the South Mountain Hiking Trails. You'll be able to have it all when you live here at Andante Apartments! Give us a call to schedule a tour of your new home. Our community features: ❖ Barbecue pavilion and picnic area ❖ Controlled-entry access ❖ Co-working lounge with complimentary Wi-Fi ❖ Dog wash and self-service grooming area ❖ Indoor/outdoor resident social lounge with demonstration kitchen and billiards table and foosball ❖ Large and small breed fenced dog parks with pet watering station ❖ Private attached garages available and reserved covered parking ❖ Relaxing resort-style pool with sundeck and spa ❖ State-of-the-art fitness center ❖ Built to Green Globes Building Certification ❖ Easy access to I-10, Loop 101, and Loop 202 ❖ Homes Wi-Fi ready with pre-installed modem/router and first month free provided by Cox ❖ Landscaped courtyard with outdoor seating ❖ Package locker with 24/7 access to packages ❖ Virtual Moving Concierge: Complimentary address change, set up home services and digital moving announcements ❖ Waived App and Admin Fees for Veterans, First Responders and Teachers ❖ Worry-free 24-hour onsite maintenance Our apartment features: ❖ 9-foot ceilings ❖ Air conditioning with programmable thermostat ❖ French doors leading to private patio ❖ Furnished apartments available ❖ In-home washer and dryer ❖ Oversized walk-in closets ❖ Polished quartz countertops ❖ Stainless steel appliances including built-in microwave, refrigerator, and dishwasher ❖ Subway tile kitchen backsplash ❖ 2-inch faux wood blinds ❖ Ceiling fans in living areas and bedrooms ❖ Deep soaker style bathtubs Get quick replies! Text or call: --