        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Scottsdale Horizon Apartments 9259 E Raintree Dr Scottsdale, AZ 85260 Monthly Price: $1820 - $2402 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Bedrooms: 2 Bathrooms: 2 Square Footage: 1006 sq ft Reach out via phone or text: show contact info Up to 4 weeks FREE when you move in by 7/15/26 on select lease terms!* *RESTRICTIONS APPLY. CONTACT US FOR DETAILS. Features in this apartment home: ✓ Furnished apartments available ✓ In-home washer and dryer ✓ Polished granite countertops ✓ Wheelchair Access in Select Units ✓ Wood-style flooring ✓ Energy-efficient appliances including built-in microwave, refrigerator, and dishwasher ✓ Mosaic tile kitchen backsplash ✓ Private balcony or patio ✓ Wheelchair Access in Select Units About the community: Your Scottsdale Horizon adventure begins with a tour of our tasteful luxury apartments. Located at the junction between Raintree Drive and 92nd and just a short walk away from the Scottsdale Horizon Center, our pet-friendly apartments are an ideal place to call home. Lounge by one of the two resort-inspired swimming pools with spa and BBQ grills, take a walk around our pet-friendly grounds to enjoy the lush and mature landscaping, or retreat to the resident lounge for some quality time with your friends. Amenities at our property: ✓ 24-hour fitness center with free weights and cardio machines ✓ Barbecue pavilion and picnic area ✓ Co-working lounge with complimentary Wi-Fi ✓ Package locker with 24/7 access to packages ✓ Reserved covered parking ✓ Resident social lounge ✓ Two resort-style pools with sundeck and spas ✓ Homes Wi-Fi ready with pre-installed modem/router and first month free provided by Cox ✓ Lush landscaped grounds ✓ Putting green ✓ Virtual Moving Concierge: Complimentary address change, set up home services and digital moving announcements ✓ Waived App and Admin Fees for Veterans, First Responders and Teachers. Additional information: Reach out via phone or text: show contact info Terms: 3-Month, 4-Month, 5-Month, 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month, 13-Month, 14-Month, 15-Month Pets: We welcome you and your pet to your new home. Before moving in, please take a moment to review our pet policy. Website: www.rentalsapts.com?n=scottsdale_horizon&rp=fk4kbY37XsB3&t=wb Online Application: www.rentalsapts.com?n=scottsdale_horizon&rp=fk4kbY37XsB3&t=ap 3D Virtual Tour: www.rentalsapts.com?n=scottsdale_horizon&rp=fk4kbY37XsB3&t=trt We only rent our apartments directly through our website or leasing office. We do not use any electronic funds transferring apps such as Zelle, Venmo, or Cashapp. All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 3C95DFC65C9C4A06",
