        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post Community Location: 900 W Grove Pky - Tempe, AZ 85283 Monthly Price: $1442 - $2256 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Apartment Details: 2 Bedroom 1 Bath | 925 sq ft Leasing Options: 3-Month, 4-Month, 5-Month, 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month, 13-Month We accept call and text messaging: show contact info 1 month FREE when you move in by 6/15/26!* *RESTRICTIONS APPLY. CONTACT US FOR DETAILS. Apartment Amenities: ❖ Air conditioning ❖ Built-in dishwasher ❖ Built-in microwave ❖ DIshwasher ❖ Energy-efficient appliances ❖ In-home washer and dryer ❖ Private patios ❖ Programmable thermostat ❖ Refrigerator ❖ Stainless steel appliances selected units ❖ 9-foot ceilings selected units ❖ Ceiling fans in living areas and bedrooms selected units ❖ Cozy, in-home fireplaces selected units ❖ Furnished apartments - service available ❖ Oversized walk-in closets ❖ Quartz inspired kitchen selected units ❖ Separate dining area ❖ Wood-style plank flooring selected units Property Features: ❖ 24-hour fitness center ❖ 3 relaxing resort-style pools ❖ Barbecue pavilion ❖ Cardio machines ❖ Free weights ❖ Onsite playground ❖ Package locker with 24/7 access to packages ❖ Pet watering station ❖ Picnic area ❖ Sundecks ❖ Arcade Room - Coming Soon* ❖ Eco-friendly community features an onsite recycling program ❖ Homes Wi-Fi ready Pre-installed modem/router and first month free provided by Cox ❖ Pet friendly (breed restrictions apply) ❖ Resident social lounge with demonstration kitchen and billiards table and shuffleboard ❖ Waived App and Admin Fees for Veterans, First Responders and Teachers. ❖ Worry-free 24-hour onsite maintenance Description: Outside of your home, you'll find a fenced dog park for your furry friend, and three relaxing pools to choose from when you want to cool down from the Arizona sun. On-site package lockers and 24-hour onsite maintenance offer peace of mind for each and every resident. Enticed? We thought you might be. Take a look at all the top tier amenities we offer at Garden Grove Apartment Homes. Pets: Pet Policy Overview Dogs and cats are welcome at our community. All pet residents must have their health check, shots and be spayed or neutered upon move-in. A signed Animal Addendum is required to be on file at our leasing office. Two (2) max pets allowed. We accept call and text messaging: show contact info Website: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=garden_grove&rp=5xyKeJFQifgR&t=wb Online Application: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=garden_grove&rp=5xyKeJFQifgR&t=ap 3D Virtual Tour: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=garden_grove&rp=5xyKeJFQifgR&t=trt We only rent our apartments directly through our website or leasing office. We do not use any electronic funds transferring apps such as Zelle, Venmo, or Cashapp. All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY EFC567EF906A427E",
