        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Sonoran Apartment Homes Monthly Price: $1380 - $1742 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. SIZE: 732 sq ft BEDROOMS: 1 BATHROOMS: 1 LEASE TERMS: 3-Month, 4-Month, 5-Month, 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month, 13-Month Text or call to schedule a viewing: show contact info Up to one month FREE on select apartments when you move in by 6/30/26!* *RESTRICTIONS APPLY. CONTACT US FOR DETAILS. APARTMENT HOME FEATURES: ● Air conditioning with programmable thermostat ● Furnished apartments available ● In-home washer and dryer ● Polished quartz countertops ● Private balcony or patio ● Stainless steel appliances including built-in microwave, refrigerator, and dishwasher ● Subway tile kitchen backsplash ● White shaker cabinetry ● 2-inch faux wood blinds ● Built-in linen closet ● Ceiling fans in living areas and bedrooms ● Cozy wood fireplaces available ● Oversized walk-in closets ● Separate dining area ● Wood-style plank flooring Our location in the Ahwatukee Foothills offers plenty of year-round activities throughout the South Mountain Preserve. Shopping, school, and work are all just a stone's throw away, allowing you to enjoy the easy life you've been dreaming of. We're close to the Ahwatukee Foothills Town Center and easy access to I10 and 202. Take a look at our Photo Gallery and then schedule a tour with us, we'd love to show you around. Contact us today! Move-in ready PROPERTY FEATURES: ● Barbecue pavilion and picnic area ● Courtesy patrol ● Event courtyard ● Heated resort-style pool with sundeck and spa ● Pet friendly (breed restrictions apply) ● Reserved covered parking ● Smoke-free community ● State-of-the-art fitness center ● Steps from Valley Metro Bus stop ● Flexible lease terms available ● Homes Wi-Fi ready with pre-installed modem/router and first month free provided by Cox ● Professional onsite management ● Virtual 