        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post Sonoran Apartment Homes Monthly Price: $1380 - $1742 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. SIZE: 732 sq ft BEDROOMS: 1 BATHROOMS: 1 LEASE TERMS: 3-Month, 4-Month, 5-Month, 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month, 13-Month Text or call to schedule a viewing: show contact info Up to one month FREE on select apartments when you move in by 6/30/26!* *RESTRICTIONS APPLY. CONTACT US FOR DETAILS. APARTMENT HOME FEATURES: ● Air conditioning with programmable thermostat ● Furnished apartments available ● In-home washer and dryer ● Polished quartz countertops ● Private balcony or patio ● Stainless steel appliances including built-in microwave, refrigerator, and dishwasher ● Subway tile kitchen backsplash ● White shaker cabinetry ● 2-inch faux wood blinds ● Built-in linen closet ● Ceiling fans in living areas and bedrooms ● Cozy wood fireplaces available ● Oversized walk-in closets ● Separate dining area ● Wood-style plank flooring Our location in the Ahwatukee Foothills offers plenty of year-round activities throughout the South Mountain Preserve. Shopping, school, and work are all just a stone's throw away, allowing you to enjoy the easy life you've been dreaming of. We're close to the Ahwatukee Foothills Town Center and easy access to I10 and 202. Take a look at our Photo Gallery and then schedule a tour with us, we'd love to show you around. Contact us today! Move-in ready PROPERTY FEATURES: ● Barbecue pavilion and picnic area ● Courtesy patrol ● Event courtyard ● Heated resort-style pool with sundeck and spa ● Pet friendly (breed restrictions apply) ● Reserved covered parking ● Smoke-free community ● State-of-the-art fitness center ● Steps from Valley Metro Bus stop ● Flexible lease terms available ● Homes Wi-Fi ready with pre-installed modem/router and first month free provided by Cox ● Professional onsite management ● Virtual Moving Concierge: Complimentary address change, set up home services and digital moving announcements ● Waived App and Admin Fees for Veterans, First Responders and Teachers. ● Worry-free 24-hour onsite maintenance PET POLICY: Dogs and cats are welcome at our community. All pet residents must have their health check, shots and be spayed or neutered upon move-in. A signed Animal Addendum is required to be on file at our leasing office. Two (2) max pets allowed. Breed restrictions apply. VISIT US TODAY! 13625 S 48th St Phoenix, AZ 85044 Text or call to schedule a viewing: show contact info Website: www.lease-apts.com?n=sonoran&rp=39Gks3WsBvu7&t=wb Online Application: www.lease-apts.com?n=sonoran&rp=39Gks3WsBvu7&t=ap 3D Virtual Tour: www.lease-apts.com?n=sonoran&rp=39Gks3WsBvu7&t=trt We only rent our apartments directly through our website or leasing office. We do not use any electronic funds transferring apps such as Zelle, Venmo, or Cashapp. All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 86CF54323501483D",
