        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post 2150 Apartments Bedroom: 1 | Bathroom: 1 Square Footage: 681 sq ft Monthly Price: $1277 - $1673 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Contact us for more information! show contact info Up to 8 weeks FREE when you lease by 7/15/26!* *RESTRICTIONS APPLY. CONTACT US FOR DETAILS. Community Description Our spacious floor plans offer apartment living with an attached garage, ensuring that our community is designed specifically to ensure you don't just rent, you live. Come experience apartment living like you've never seen right in the heart of Chandler! Community Amenities ✓ Barbecue pavilion and picnic area ✓ Basketball court ✓ Controlled-entry access ✓ Dedicated covered parking available ✓ Easy access to Loop 202 ✓ Fenced dog park with pet watering station ✓ Onsite playground ✓ State-of-the-art fitness center ✓ Homes Wi-Fi ready with pre-installed modem/router and first month free provided by Cox ✓ Package locker with 24/7 access to packages ✓ Relaxing resort-style pool with sundeck and spa ✓ Resident social lounge with demonstration kitchen and media room ✓ Virtual moving concierge - Complimentary address change, set up home services and digital moving announcements ✓ Waived App and Admin Fees for Veterans, First Responders and Teachers. Apartment Features ✓ 9-foot ceilings ✓ In-home washer and dryer ✓ Kitchen breakfast bar ✓ Oversized walk-in closets ✓ Private balcony or patio ✓ Air conditioning with programmable thermostat ✓ Furnished apartments available ✓ Polished quartz and granite countertops ✓ Stainless steel appliances including built-in microwave, refrigerator, and dishwasher ✓ Wood-style plank flooring Contact Information Visit Us: 2150 S Arizona Ave Chandler, AZ 85286 Contact us for more information! show contact info Hours: Mon - Fri: 9:00 AM - 6:00 PM Sat - Sun: 10:00 AM - 5:00 PM Website: www.lease-apts.com?n=2150&rp=j9gVT7knknDe&t=wb Online Application: www.lease-apts.com?n=2150&rp=j9gVT7knknDe&t=ap 3D Virtual Tour: www.lease-apts.com?n=2150&rp=j9gVT7knknDe&t=trt Additional Details Pet Policy: Dogs and cats are welcome at our community. All pet residents must have their health check, shots and be spayed or neutered upon move-in. A signed Animal Addendum is required to be on file at our leasing office. Two (2) max pets allowed. Lease Terms: 3-Month, 4-Month, 5-Month, 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month, 13-Month, 14-Month We only rent our apartments directly through our website or leasing office. We do not use any electronic funds transferring apps such as Zelle, Venmo, or Cashapp. All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 9D86604723DC4C9",
