        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post Elevate at Discovery Park 1820 E Bell De Mar Dr Tempe, AZ 85283 Monthly Price: $1666 - $2042 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Bedrooms: 2 Bathrooms: 2 Square Footage: 1190 sq ft Text or call for details at show contact info Features in this apartment home: ✓ Air conditioning with programmable thermostat ✓ Energy-efficient appliances including built-in microwave, refrigerator, and dishwasher ✓ In-home washer and dryer ✓ Oversized walk-in closets ✓ Polished granite kitchen countertops ✓ Private balcony or patio ✓ Separate dining area ✓ Wood-style plank flooring ✓ Ceiling fans in living areas and bedrooms ✓ Courtyard and pool views ✓ Fireplaces available ✓ Vaulted ceilings About the community: Conveniently located in the heart of Tempe, Arizona, just south of the Arizona Canal, residents of Elevate at Discovery Park can enjoy nearby parks, exceptional local cuisine, shopping, and nightlife, all while taking advantage of incredible access to Valley freeways, top-rated school systems, and Arizona State University. Amenities at our property: ✓ 24-hour fitness center with free weights and cardio machines ✓ Fenced dog park with pet watering station ✓ On-site professional management team ✓ Relaxing resort-style pool with sundeck and spa ✓ Reserved covered parking ✓ Terrace featuring fire pit, barbecue pavilion, and picnic area ✓ Walking distance to dining, shopping, and nightlife ✓ Worry-free 24-hour onsite maintenance ✓ Easy access to public transportation ✓ Easy access to U.S. 60, Loop 101, and I-10 Freeway Systems ✓ Flexible lease terms available ✓ Homes Wi-Fi ready with pre-installed modem/router and first month free provided by Cox ✓ Less than 5 miles from Arizona State University ✓ Onsite access to Tempe Stroud Park ✓ Pet friendly (breed restrictions apply) Additional information: Text or call for details at show contact info Terms: 3-Month, 4-Month, 5-Month, 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month, 13-Month, 14-Month, 15-Month, 16-Month Pets: Dogs and cats are welcome at our community. All pet residents must have their health check, shots and be spayed or neutered upon move-in. A signed Animal Addendum is required to be on file at our leasing office. Two (2) max pets allowed. Website: www.lease-apts.com?n=elevate_at_discovery_park&rp=k2dipQ4gKex7&t=wb Online Application: www.lease-apts.com?n=elevate_at_discovery_park&rp=k2dipQ4gKex7&t=ap 3D Virtual Tour: www.lease-apts.com?n=elevate_at_discovery_park&rp=k2dipQ4gKex7&t=trt We only rent our apartments directly through our website or leasing office. We do not use any electronic funds transferring apps such as Zelle, Venmo, or Cashapp. All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 920168051CAF46",
