        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post IMT Riverview 711 N Evergreen Road Mesa, AZ 85201 Office Phone: show contact info LOOK & LEASE: Receive 1 month free rent when you apply within 24 hours of your tour.* *Restrictions apply; offer subject to change at any time. Offer expires on 06/29/26. Special offer only applies to base rent and not any fees included in Total Monthly Price. Credit will apply to the second full month’s statement. Special excludes all property transfers and current residents. 12-month minimum lease term applies. Apartment Information: 2 Bedroom | 2 Bath Apartment Size: 1211 sq ft Monthly Price: $1988 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Lease Terms: 3-Month, 4-Month, 5-Month, 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month Apartment Includes: ✓ Built-in Linen Closets In Select Homes ✓ Ceramic Tile Flooring In Select Homes ✓ Decorative Crown Molding ✓ Full-size Washer/Dryer in Each Home ✓ Fully Equipped Kitchens, Including Microwave & Ref ✓ Garden-style Soaking Tub ✓ Nine-foot Ceilings ✓ Personal Storage Space In Select Homes ✓ Pre-installed WiFi with 1st Month Free from Cox ✓ Spacious Private Patio or Balcony Property Description: **Walk-ins welcome & choose from 3 tour options.** Welcome to IMT Riverview, strategically situated apartments in Mesa, AZ while at the doorstep of thriving Tempe. Surrounded by a foodie's utopia of restaurants plus great shopping and entertainment at Mesa Riverview and Tempe Marketplace just outside your door. Enjoy coming home to the lush landscaping, an abundance of community amenities and well-appointed one and two bedroom apartment homes complete with all the conveniences you desire. Take a Virtual Tour of Our Property Today! https://liveimt.com/imtRiverviewYoutubeTour Price shown is Total Monthly Price including monthly mandatory fees* Mandatory Fees: - Package Locker: $5/month - Credit Reporting: $5/month - Service Fee: $3/month - Sewer Charge: Varies - Trash: Varies - Water Charges: Varies Property Amenities: ✓ Accepts Credit Card Payments ✓ Assigned Parking ✓ Coffee Bar ✓ Common Area Wi-Fi ✓ Disability Access ✓ On-line Maintenance Request ✓ On-Line Payments ✓ Recycling Available ✓ Shopping Nearby ✓ Swimming Pool ✓ Apache Light Rail Station one mile ✓ Conference Room & High-Tech Business Center ✓ Convenient freeway access to the 101 and 202 ✓ Fireside lounge ✓ Fitness Center with Cardio & Weight Training Equipment ✓ Near Tempe Market Place and Mesa Riverview ✓ Private garages or covered parking available ✓ Resort-style aquamarine pool and spa ✓ Shaded conversation lanais and lush green courtyards ✓ Spacious outdoor entertainment space with beautiful picnic areas Website: www.lease-apts.com?n=imt_riverview&rp=3eUp5ogXNUn1&t=wb Office Phone: show contact info Mon - Fri: 8:30 AM - 5:30 PM Sat: 10:00 AM - 5:00 PM Sun: 11:00 AM - 4:00 PM Pet Ownership Policy: At IMT Riverview, we know that the path to your heart is marked with paw prints and that the best part of your day is coming home to a wagging tail. Pets are residents too! Pets Welcome! Two pets maximum $300 Pet Fee/$30 monthly Pet Rent per pet No weight limit. Breed restrictions apply. *Total Monthly Price includes base rent, all monthly mandatory and any user-selected optional fees. Excludes variable, usage-based, and required charges due at or prior to move-in or at move-out. Discounts, if applicable, will be calculated upon lease execution. Minimum lease terms and occupancy guidelines may apply. Deposits may vary based on credit, rental history, income, or other qualifying criteria. Additional fees and taxes may apply and will be disclosed per governing laws and company policies. Total Monthly Price may be displayed as a whole dollar amount for advertising purposes only; actual charges are calculated using exact fee amounts, including cents, and may vary from the displayed amount by up to 50 cents due to rounding. Mandatory Fees: - Package Locker: $5/month - Credit Reporting: $5/month - Service Fee: $3/month - Sewer Charge: Varies - Trash: Varies - Water Charges: Varies All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY FD2F48685E8346A",
