        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post RENTAL INFO Monthly Price: $1896 - $3128 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Biscayne Bay Apartments: 300 E Warner Rd Chandler, AZ 85225 Apartment for Rent: 3-BR 2-BA | Square Feet: 1320 sq ft | Lease Length: 3-Month, 4-Month, 5-Month, 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month, 13-Month, 14-Month Call us today at show contact info Up to 4 weeks FREE when you move in by 6/30/26!* *RESTRICTIONS APPLY. CONTACT US FOR DETAILS. PROPERTY AMENITIES − Fenced dog park − Indoor/outdoor poolside kitchen − NEW Expansive pool deck − Package locker with 24/7 access to packages − Pet friendly (breed restrictions apply) − Private garages with remotes − Two resort-style pools with sundeck and spa − Two story state-of-the-art fitness center − Worry-free 24-hour onsite maintenance − Basketball court − Controlled-entry access − Co-working lounge with complimentary Wi-Fi − Gilbert School District − Homes Wi-Fi ready with pre-installed modem/router and first month free provided by Cox − Lush landscaped grounds − Separate storage units available − Virtual Moving Concierge: Complimentary address change, set up home services and digital moving announcements − Waived App and Admin Fees for Veterans, First Responders and Teachers. APARTMENT AMENITIES − 9-foot ceilings − Furnished apartments available − In-home washer and dryer − Polished steel quartz kitchen countertops − Private balcony or patio − Stainless steel appliances − Upgraded energy-saving lighting package − Wheelchair Access in Select Homes − Wood-style plank flooring in kitchen and living areas − Air conditioning − Breakfast bar − Crown molding − Oversized dual-pane windows − Oversized walk-in closets − Spacious pantries − USB charging outlets − White cabinets with brushed nickel door pulls in upgraded apartments ADDITIONAL INFO Description: Natural and refined. Warm and inviting. Versatile and timeless. Explore our gallery and imagine the life that awaits in our stunning, refined apartments. Schedule a private tour to experience Biscayne Bay Apartments for yourself! Take a few moments to view our floor plans and apply below before your next home is taken or take an in-person tour to experience it for yourself! Our friendly, professional staff would be ecstatic to assist you and show you why your Biscayne Bay isn't just another apartment, it's your new home! Pet Policy: Dogs and cats are welcome at our community. All pet residents must have their health check, shots and be spayed or neutered upon move-in. A signed Animal Addendum is required to be on file at our leasing office. Two (2) max pets allowed. Breed Restrictions Apply. Website: www.apt-rental.com?n=biscayne_bay&rp=himKTAQZfaEP&t=wb Online Application: www.apt-rental.com?n=biscayne_bay&rp=himKTAQZfaEP&t=ap 3D Virtual Tour: www.apt-rental.com?n=biscayne_bay&rp=himKTAQZfaEP&t=trt Call us today at show contact info We only rent our apartments directly through our website or leasing office. We do not use any electronic funds transferring apps such as Zelle, Venmo, or Cashapp. All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 983BED8F304C48",
