        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post NOVO Broadway Featured Floorplan: 3-bed / 2-bath / 1262 sq ft Monthly Price: $2608 - $3310 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Deposit: Call Call us today at show contact info Description: NOVO Broadway provides the ideal space to live, work, create, play, and relax right in the heart of Tempe. You'll look forward to coming home every day to your new home beautifully outfitted with gourmet kitchens, stainless steel appliances, and wood-style flooring. This coupled with conveniences like in-home laundry and vaulted ceilings makes NOVO Broadway feel both modern and refined. Move in special: Up to 8 weeks free 2 bedroom BLOWOUT! Up to 8 weeks free when you apply by 6/30/2026!* *RESTRICTIONS APPLY. CONTACT US FOR DETAILS. Lease Terms: 3-Month, 4-Month, 5-Month, 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month, 13-Month Pet Policy: We welcome you and your pet to your new home. Before moving in, please take a moment to review our pet policy. Apartment Amenities: ◾ 9-14 foot ceilings ◾ Air conditioning ◾ Dual-pane windows ◾ Oversized closets ◾ Private patio or balcony ◾ Stainless steel appliances ◾ USB charging ports ◾ Ceiling fans with integrated lighting ◾ Furnished apartments available ◾ Gourmet kitchens with granite countertops ◾ In-home washer and dryer ◾ Luxurious bathrooms with high-end finishes ◾ Wood-style plank flooring with carpet in bedrooms Community Features: ◾ Barbecue pavilion ◾ Camelback Mountain views ◾ Controlled-entry access ◾ Co-working lounge ◾ Dog park and pet wash station ◾ Easy freeway access ◾ Elevator access ◾ EV car charging stations ◾ Outdoor fire pit lounge area ◾ Reserved covered parking ◾ 24-hour fitness center with free weights and cardio machines ◾ Indoor mailroom with Amazon parcel lockers ◾ Move-in with NO SECURITY DEPOSIT: Only a small one-time payment ◾ Relaxing resort-style pool with sundeck and spa ◾ Resident social lounge with TV and coffee bar ◾ Virtual moving concierge - Complimentary address change, set up home services and digital moving announcements Address: 711 West Broadway Road Tempe, AZ 85282 Call us today at show contact info Mon - Fri: 9:00 AM - 6:00 PM Sat - Sun: 10:00 AM - 5:00 PM Website: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=novo_broadway&rp=hkhEVdeXQoN6&t=wb Online Application: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=novo_broadway&rp=hkhEVdeXQoN6&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=novo_broadway&rp=hkhEVdeXQoN6&t=sch We only rent our apartments directly through our website or leasing office. We do not use any electronic funds transferring apps such as Zelle, Venmo, or Cashapp. All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY ED4B7913D01D401",
