ident social lounge with TV and coffee bar ◾ Virtual moving concierge - Complimentary address change, set up home services and digital moving announcements Address: 711 West Broadway Road Tempe, AZ 85282 Call us today at show contact info Mon - Fri: 9:00 AM - 6:00 PM Sat - Sun: 10:00 AM - 5:00 PM Website: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=novo_broadway&rp=hkhEVdeXQoN6&t=wb Online Application: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=novo_broadway&rp=hkhEVdeXQoN6&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=novo_broadway&rp=hkhEVdeXQoN6&t=sch We only rent our apartments directly through our website or leasing office. We do not use any electronic funds transferring apps such as Zelle, Venmo, or Cashapp. All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY ED4B7913D01D401",
