        "geocode_query": "3601 N Central Ave",
        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Centra Midtown Address: 3601 N Central Ave Phoenix, AZ 85012 Monthly Price: $1953 - $2424 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Bedrooms: 2 | Baths: 2 | Sq. Footage: 1069 sq ft | Terms: 3-Month, 4-Month, 5-Month, 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month, 13-Month, 14-Month, 15-Month Text or call for details at show contact info + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + Features in this apartment home: ✓ Air conditioning with programmable thermostat ✓ French doors leading to a private balcony or patio ✓ Full size in-home washer and dryer ✓ Furnished apartments available ✓ Kitchen island with pendant lighting ✓ Luxury kitchen tile backsplash ✓ Polished granite countertops ✓ Stainless steel appliances including built-in microwave, refrigerator, gas range, and dishwasher ✓ Wood-style plank flooring in kitchen and living areas ✓ 2-inch faux wood blinds ✓ Ceiling fans in living areas and bedrooms ✓ Deep soaker style bathtubs ✓ Elevator access ✓ Keyless smart lock technology ✓ Oversized walk-in closets ✓ Separate shower with glass enclosure + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + Amenities at our property: ✓ Barbecue pavilion, mini-golf, and outdoor fire pit ✓ Dog run- we welcome furry friends! ✓ Pet friendly (breed restrictions apply) ✓ Relaxing resort-style pool with sundeck cabanas and spa ✓ Resident social lounge and game room with demonstration kitchen, billiards table, shuffleboard table, and arcade games ✓ Rooftop lounge with panoramic city views ✓ State-of-the-art fitness center with yoga, spin, and cross-fit rooms ✓ Underground gated parking garage with direct access elevators ✓ Built to LEED® Certification ✓ Homes Wi-Fi ready with pre-installed modem/router and first month free provided by Cox ✓ Package locker with 24/7 access to packages ✓ Seconds the from Light Rail station ✓ Virtual moving concierge - Complimentary address change, set up home services and digital moving announcements ✓ Waived App and Admin Fees for Veterans, First Responders, Teachers, and Creighton University students, Pending Application Approval ✓ Walk Score 74 and Bike Score 74 + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + About the community: A premier amenity package shaped for convenience, we offer access to our year-round energizing pool, outdoor cabanas and entertainment area, cool social lounge spaces, a high-intensity training studio, and the ultimate rooftop deck with unbeatable city views! In your apartment, unwind and cozy up with our spacious, interior comforts offering the latest in design and attractive modern finishes. You will love our ultra-modern amenities that make any day that much easier. If you're looking for an apartment community that provides you an excellent location, comfort, and convenience, then look no further than our 1 and 2 bedroom apartments in Midtown Phoenix! Pets: Dogs and cats are welcome at our community. All pet residents must have their health check, shots and be spayed or neutered upon move-in. A signed Animal Addendum is required to be on file at our leasing office. Two (2) max pets allowed. Breed restrictions apply. Text or call for details at show contact info Hours: Mon - Fri: 9:00 AM - 6:00 PM Sat - Sun: 10:00 AM - 5:00 PM Website: www.apt-rental.com?n=centra_midtown&rp=7sbMkEhZ6eo3&t=wb Online Application: www.apt-rental.com?n=centra_midtown&rp=7sbMkEhZ6eo3&t=ap 3D Virtual Tour: www.apt-rental.com?n=centra_midtown&rp=7sbMkEhZ6eo3&t=trt We only rent our apartments directly through our website or leasing office. We do not use any electronic funds transferring apps such as Zelle, Venmo, or Cashapp. All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY A9E7DE27E51A4CD",
