ess to packages ✓ Seconds the from Light Rail station ✓ Virtual moving concierge - Complimentary address change, set up home services and digital moving announcements ✓ Waived App and Admin Fees for Veterans, First Responders, Teachers, and Creighton University students, Pending Application Approval ✓ Walk Score 74 and Bike Score 74 + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + About the community: A premier amenity package shaped for convenience, we offer access to our year-round energizing pool, outdoor cabanas and entertainment area, cool social lounge spaces, a high-intensity training studio, and the ultimate rooftop deck with unbeatable city views! In your apartment, unwind and cozy up with our spacious, interior comforts offering the latest in design and attractive modern finishes. You will love our ultra-modern amenities that make any day that much easier. If you're looking for an apartment community that provides you an excellent location, comfort, and convenience, then look no further than our 1 and 2 bedroom apartments in Midtown Phoenix! Pets: Dogs and cats are welcome at our community. All pet residents must have their health check, shots and be spayed or neutered upon move-in. A signed Animal Addendum is required to be on file at our leasing office. Two (2) max pets allowed. Breed restrictions apply. Text or call for details at show contact info Hours: Mon - Fri: 9:00 AM - 6:00 PM Sat - Sun: 10:00 AM - 5:00 PM Website: www.apt-rental.com?n=centra_midtown&rp=7sbMkEhZ6eo3&t=wb Online Application: www.apt-rental.com?n=centra_midtown&rp=7sbMkEhZ6eo3&t=ap 3D Virtual Tour: www.apt-rental.com?n=centra_midtown&rp=7sbMkEhZ6eo3&t=trt We only rent our apartments directly through our website or leasing office. We do not use any electronic funds transferring apps such as Zelle, Venmo, or Cashapp. All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY A9E7DE27E51A4CD",
