        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post Welcome home to Steeple Chase! Located at: 8610 N 91st Ave Peoria, AZ 85345 Rental Information: # of Bedrooms: 2 - 3 # of Bathrooms: 2.5 Square Footage: 942 - 1190 sq ft Monthly Price: $1412 - $1626 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Call our office at show contact info \"Currently fully leased. Accepting inquiries for future available units.\" Each of our 2 & 3 bedroom apartments for rent in Peoria, Arizona, are designed to cater to your active lifestyle with quality features that include air conditioning and dishwasher. Meanwhile, community amenities like laundry facility and online rental payments are sure to keep your entertainment level high. Community Features: ➢ Carport Parking Available ➢ Laundry Facility ➢ Online Rental Payments ➢ On-Site Management ➢ Wi-Fi Available in Common Areas ➢ Fitness Center ➢ Playground ➢ Spanish Speaking Staff ➢ Swimming Pool with Hot Tub Apartment Home Features: ➢ Cable Ready ➢ Complete Appliance Package ➢ Dishwasher ➢ Private Balcony/Patio Office Hours: Mon - Fri: 8:30 AM - 5:00 PM Call our office at show contact info Pet Policy: Max Number of Pets: 2 Max Weight of Pets: 45 pounds Pet Deposit: $300 Monthly Pet Rent: $35 Leasing Options: 12-Month Website: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=steeple_chase&rp=uQfCyF1YT4zX&t=wb Income Restrictions for Steeple Chase # Occupants   -   Max Income       1 Person   -   $47,160       2 People   -   $53,820       3 People   -   $60,600       4 People   -   $67,320       5 People   -   $72,720       6 People   -   $78,120       7 People   -   $83,520       8 People   -   $88,920 To qualify, annual income must be equal or below those in the chart, based on the total number of occupants. Contact the leasing office for more information. All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 7NDHXJSCC33H8NN",
