        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Avalon Hills 3535 West Tierra Buena Lane, Phoenix, AZ, 85053 Call Now - show contact info x 112 OR Text 112 to show contact info to contact our leasing team. More unit details at: https://avenue5.aptfeatures.com/a6xcfy Modern Comfort & Style in North Phoenix 1 bedroom | 1 bath | 625 square feet Features ✓  Pre-Installed WiFi with First Month Free From COX ✓  Dishwasher ✓  Semi-Private Patios & Balconies ✓  Spacious Closets ✓  Carpet and Vinyl Flooring ✓  Ceiling Fans ✓  Frost-Free Refrigerator ✓  Extra Storage ✓  Cable & Internet Ready ✓  Stackable Washer/Dryer* ✓  Electric Appliances ✓  Close to I-17 & 101 Loop ✓  Window Coverings ✓  Built-In Computer Desk* ✓  Central A/C Community Features ✓  Spanish Speaking Staff ✓  Convenient Freeway Access ✓  On Bus Line ✓  Lush Landscaping ✓  Uncovered Parking Available ✓  Sundeck ✓  2 Laundry Facilities ✓  High Speed Internet Available ✓  Outdoor Fitness Obstacles ✓  BBQ/Picnic Area ✓  BILT Rewards ✓  On-Site Management ✓  Refreshing Pool ✓  Close to Arrowhead Mall & Westgate Entertainment District ✓  Close to Shopping & Dining ✓  Side Street Parking Available ✓  Playground ✓  Two Whirlpool Spas ✓  Assigned Covered Parking ✓  Fitness Center ✓  Clubhouse with Shuffleboard Table ✓  WiFi Hotspot in Clubhouse/Pool Area ✓  Online Payments Available ✓  VIP Package Delivery Service Community Info Experience pet-friendly living with resort-style perks - steps from Arrowhead Mall and Westgate. Located in beautiful Phoenix, Arizona Avalon Hills has the perfect apartment home for you! Choose from any of our spacious floor plans; The Acacia, the Mesquite, The Indigo or The Ocotillo. Simply step out your front door for a day of shopping or just relax in the comfort of your new home. Our professional on-site team is waiting to assist you so come in TODAY! Pet Policy Max 2 Allowed | One time Fee $300 Rent $35 | Deposit $300 Comments: Breed restrictions apply, please contact for details. Pet Rent: $35 (1 pet) OR $50 (2 pets). Office Hours Monday-Friday: 9:00AM-6:00PM Saturday: 10:00AM-5:00PM Equal Housing Opportunity GtF9SGSa14Sy",
